1
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:28,140
「天之涯」
"To the end of horizon,"

2
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:31,550
「地之角」
"four corners of Earth,"

3
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:37,350
「知交半零落」
"scattered one's true friends"

4
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:43,350
「一壶浊酒尽余欢」
"A bottle of wine for remaining joy,"

5
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:48,790
「夕阳山外山」
"as sun sets among the mountains."

6
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,670
好 好好
Brilliant...

7
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,710
汤师爷
Counselor!

8
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,510
是好吃 还是好听？
You prefer the food or my singing?

9
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,590
也好听 也好吃
I love them both!

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,550
都好 都好！
Outstanding!

11
00:01:57,720 --> 00:02:00,100
我马某走南闯北
Brain and brawn have helped me far,

12
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:03,750
靠的就是能文能武 与众不同
that's why I am so unique!

13
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:08,030
不光吃喝玩乐 更要雪月风花
One must learn to live in style!

14
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:14,830
马县长此番风度
Governor, with your style and poise,

15
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,750
正好比
you remind me of...

16
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:22,270
大风起兮云飞扬
a modern-day Robin Hood!

17
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:23,430
屁！
Bullshit!

18
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,910
刘邦是个小人！
Robin Hood is a common thief!

19
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,990
力拔山兮气盖世
with Samson's might and Solomon's wisdom!

20
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,670
屁！屁 屁
- Bullshit! - Yes, bullshit!

21
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,790
汤师爷
Counselor,

22
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,030
你要是拍我马屁
if you're trying to flatter me,

23
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:35,760
就先要先过夫人这一关
you must first woo my wife!

24
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,230
写首诗 写首诗！
Compose a poem in her honour.

25
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:41,230
要有风 要有肉
It must have a tempest, food,

26
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,590
要有火锅 要有雾
a hotpot, some mist,

27
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:46,590
要有美女 要有驴！
pretty maidens, and a mule!

28
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,390
起来 起来 起来
Get up!

29
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,990
一起吃！一起唱！
Let's eat, sing and be merry!

30
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:03,910
报告县长！我们铁血十八星陆军
Sir, we are the elite Republican Guards,

31
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,830
护送县长安全上任！
here to ensure your safe passage!

32
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,790
我们…
We -

33
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,630
不吃饭！
don't - need - to - eat!

34
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,980
没打中？
You missed?

35
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,110
让子弹飞一会儿
Let the bullets fly...

36
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,500
老二老三跟我走
Two and Three come with me.

37
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,190
其他人把白马抓回来！
The rest round up the horses.

38
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,780
火锅？
Raining hot pot?

39
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,790
爹 全都找遍了
Pop, we've looked all over.

40
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,750
没钱 没货 也没有银子
There is absolutely nothing!

41
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,230
人倒是剩两活的 杀不杀？
Should we just kill the two survivors?

42
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,750
钱藏在哪儿了？说出来
Tell me where the money is?

43
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,790
闹钟响之前要是说不出来
Or I'll cut off your head,

44
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,830
脑袋搬家
when the alarm goes off.

45
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,780
哭？
Stop it!

46
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,990
哭也算时间啊
Tears won't stop it from ticking.

47
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,150
有什么就说什么嘛
You'd better come clean with them.

48
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,430
这位夫人 你是谁？
Who might you be, ma'am?

49
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,070
我就是县长夫人啊
I'm the Governor's wife.

50
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,670
失敬！失敬！
Forgive my impudence.

51
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,670
那你就是县太爷？
So you must be the Governor.

52
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:46,310
有钱！有钱…！
Yes, of course! There's money!

53
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,660
我跟县长进城上任
We're on our way to inauguration.

54
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,150
县长淹死了 现在没有
He ruined it all by getting drowned!

55
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,990
上任就有！上任就有钱
But we can still hit jackpot

56
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,670
上任就有！
if we take his vacant post.

57
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,790
再给你一圈 顺着买官往下说
I'll give you another chance. Tell me more.

58
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,430
有二十万
$200,000...

59
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,590
-钱呢？      -买官了
- Where is it? - Bought the post with it.

60
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,790
-买官干什么？     -赚钱
- What for? - To make more money.

61
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,020
-能赚多少？     -一倍
- How much? - Twice as much.

62
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,260
-多长时间？     -一年
- How long will it take? - A year.

63
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,660
我要等你一年？
I've to wait one year?

64
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:07,110
半年半年！手气好 一个月也行！
A month, if you're in luck.

65
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,990
-县长淹死了 谁去上任？     -我!
- Who will be the governor? - Me.

66
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,070
-你是谁？     -师爷
- And who might you be? - I'm a counselor.

67
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,430
你一个师爷敢冒充县长？
You dare to impersonate the Governor?

68
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,630
没人认识县长长什么模样
They've never met him.

69
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,150
-你干过几次？     -一年两次
- Done this before? - Twice a year.

70
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:17,260
-干过几年？     -八年
- Since when? - Eight years ago.

71
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:20,510
八八六十四 你赚过六百四十万？
You've made more than $6.4 million?

72
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,790
他 他县长赚过六百四十万！
That's what the "Governor" made.

73
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:25,190
我不是师爷么 我就赚个零头！
I only get the small change.

74
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,030
没失过手？
Ever failed?

75
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,190
不动手 拼的是脑子 不流血
We use our brains, not brawn.

76
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,670
你这次去哪儿上任？
Where are you heading to?

77
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,950
鹅城
Goose Town.

78
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:33,110
火车被劫 你的人淹死了怎么交代？
How do you explain the hold-up and the bodies?

79
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:35,660
车是我买的 人是我雇的 没人追查
I bought the train and hired the soldiers.

80
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,190
没有人追查
No one will ever find out.

81
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,350
别摘！别摘…！千万别摘！
Don't take it off! Leave your mask on!

82
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,150
规矩我懂
I know the rules.

83
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,380
看见你的脸我就活不成
No one lives after seeing a bandit's face.

84
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,310
你把我放了 我上任鹅城
Just wait here for me.

85
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,350
赚了钱 都给你！都给你！
I'll bring you the money once I have it.

86
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,590
弟兄们劫回道
We came to rob a train,

87
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,750
一分钱都没捞着 不合适吧
we can't go empty-handed.

88
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,510
不合适
No, you can't.

89
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,980
你看了我一眼小命就丢了 也不合适吧
If you die for peeking at me...

90
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,420
更不合适
That's even worse.

91
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,390
你那些淹死的兄弟给我用用？
Can I borrow those bodies?

92
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,190
用！...他们欺男霸女 死有余辜！
Yes. These bullies deserve no better.

93
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,110
不是 死了有什么用啊？
But what do you want to do with them?

94
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:02,510
死人有时候比活人有用
They can be more useful than the living.

95
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:05,030
师爷 睁开眼看我一眼
Take a look at me.

96
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,630
看一眼
Look at me!

97
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,550
就看一眼
Just one look!

98
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,230
师爷贵姓？别客气
- What's your name? - I...

99
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:12,150
姓什么？姓汤
- What's your bloody name? - Tang.

100
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,830
汤师爷 我当县长
I'll be the Governor,

101
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,190
你继续当我的师爷
and you'll be my counselor!

102
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,580
咱们鹅城走一趟
Let's go and rule Goose Town.

103
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,550
夫人 要不要走一趟？
Ma'am, coming with us?

104
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,350
走就走嘛
Well, why not?

105
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:24,950
嘿嘿嘿 弟兄们上任鹅城
Brothers, let's move on to Goose Town!

106
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,680
上任鹅城！
Goose Town here we come!

107
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,540
兄弟们失了手
We've messed up badly.

108
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:33,070
让你丈夫横遭了不测
End up drowning your husband.

109
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,540
我很是愧疚
I feel bad about it.

110
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,350
我已经第四次当寡妇了
I've already been widowed four times.

111
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,230
那可千万别第五次哦！
Don't let there be a fifth time, then!

112
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,030
那就要看你的本事了
That's all up to you.

113
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:44,430
师爷 当夫妻最要紧的是什么？
What's important for a couple?

114
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,590
恩爱！
In love.

115
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,350
听不见 再说一遍
I can't hear you.

116
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,710
恩爱！
In love.

117
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,020
来 见过母亲大人
Six, come greet your Mom.

118
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,390
母亲大人好 小六子有礼了！
I wish you well, Mother.

119
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,590
你出生入死 还带着儿子啊？
You bring your son to battles?

120
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,830
他爹是我的兄弟 阵亡了
His father was a comrade. Died in battle.

121
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,870
所以他就成了我的儿子
So I adopted him as my god son.

122
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,110
所以呢 你现在就是我的母亲大人！
Now you're my mother.

123
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,260
等这桩买卖做完后
After we're done with Goose Town,

124
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,630
跟我们一块回山里吧
you must come and join our gang.

125
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,910
你可以继续当我的母亲
Then you can continue to play mother.

126
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,910
人往高处走 水往低处流！
One should always aim high.

127
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,270
当惯了县长
After serving as county governor,

128
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,540
再回去当麻匪
I can't return to banditry.

129
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,030
恐怕会有点不习惯吧
I won't be able to handle it.

130
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,990
曾经沧海难为水嘛
Once you've scaled Mount Everest...

131
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,070
说得好
Such eloquence!

132
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:15,260
那怎么办啊？
Then what should we do?

133
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,910
「从正面绕回来 让大家乐一乐」
"Bring him back from the front for a laugh!"

134
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,990
怎么办？继续当官呗！
We can continue to be civil servants!

135
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,900
遇事要多动脑筋
Use your brain, not brawn.

136
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,750
先动脑子后动手 明白吗？
Think twice before you make a move.

137
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,060
明白
Got it.

138
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,110
师爷
Counselor!

139
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:33,310
我们现在是做官的人了
We're government officials now.

140
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,740
不得再有匪气
We can't act like bandits!

141
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:37,300
师爷 当县长最要紧的是什么？
What is a good governor's virtue?

142
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:38,790
忍耐！
Forbearance.

143
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,510
"Goose Town"

144
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:43,990
你逃过一次
You've escaped once.

145
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,350
你要是再敢耍我…
Try this one more time...

146
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,940
明白！脑袋搬家
You'll have me beheaded!

147
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,430
进城
Let's go!

148
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,550
城里的女人就是白啊
City girls are so fair and delicate!

149
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,270
"Wanted, Dead or Alive!"

150
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,110
爹 你看
Pop, look!

151
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,670
他们怎么把你画成这样了！
Look what they've made of you!

152
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,510
越不像越安全
The less it resembles me, the safer I am!

153
00:09:57,880 --> 00:10:01,190
恭迎县长大人！
Welcome, your honour!

154
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:04,550
委任状！
Appointment Warrant!

155
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:09,390
兹委任马邦德为鹅县县长
Ma Bangde is appointed Goose Town Governor

156
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:15,590
此状 中华民国萨南康省主席巴青泰
by authority of the Provincial Chairman,

157
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:20,390
中华民国八年八月二十八日
on this 28th day of February,
the 8th year of the Republic...

158
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:24,230
黄老爷驾到
Master Huang has arrived!

159
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:30,710
黄老爷吉祥！
Greetings to Master Huang!
Good fortune to Master Huang!

160
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:33,440
此乃南国一霸黄四郎
Huang Silang is the local godfather.

161
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:37,430
干的是贩卖人口 倒卖烟土的大生意
Made his fortune from opium and human trafficking.

162
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,550
黄老爷百忙无暇
Master is currently engaged.

163
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,750
特命我黄府大管家胡万！
So he sends his majordomo, Hu Wan!

164
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,790
黄府团练教头武智冲！
And his militia coach, Wu Zhichong!

165
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:48,430
礼帽 礼貌 欢迎县长！
To welcome you, sir, with his hat!

166
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:52,750
来者不善啊
Who dares win!

167
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:55,910
你才是来者
Do you dare?

168
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:11,670
老爷 来了
He's here, sir.

169
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,670
谁呀？
Who's here?

170
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,550
你自己
Yourself!

171
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,910
黄大爷万寿！
Long live Master Huang!

172
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,540
小的杨万楼 这厢有礼
Greetings from Yang Wanlou!

173
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,710
赝品是个好东西！
A remarkable fake!

174
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:23,230
赝品是个好东西！
A remarkable fake!

175
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:25,390
走几步
Take a few steps.

176
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:28,590
走出个虎虎生风
Walk purposefully.

177
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:31,270
走个虎虎生风
Purposefully...

178
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,510
走出一个一日千里
Walk with spirit.

179
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:35,390
走个一日千里
Spiritedly...

180
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,590
走出一个恍如隔世
Walk pensively.

181
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,990
走个恍如隔世
Pensively...

182
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,350
你说她怎么不害怕啊？
Why isn't she afraid?

183
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,950
有点傻吧
She must be daft.

184
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,670
为什么要枪毙麻匪？
Know why we shot these bandits?

185
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,750
因为他们抢官车 劫县长！
It's because they ambushed the Governor.

186
00:11:57,920 --> 00:12:00,550
枪毙他们 就是为了让大家明白
Let this be a lesson to all!

187
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,830
对抗官府之下场！
Never mess with the Governor!

188
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:05,870
县长来了 鹅城太平了！
Hail the Governor!

189
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:10,110
县长来了 青天就有啦！
Peace and justice is here!

190
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,910
师爷 说得好啊
Great speech!

191
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,660
你记得我跟你说过
Remember what I told you?

192
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,790
有时候死人比活人有用吧
The dead can be really handy.

193
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,750
是 死人是比活人有用
You're absolutely right.

194
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,830
霸气外露！
Such arrogance!

195
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,670
找死！
He's trouble.

196
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,550
刚进城就开枪
A show of force!

197
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:39,390
这不是二八开能打发走的
This one is a tricky customer!

198
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,030
先发制人？
Should we strike first?

199
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,030
不急
No hurry.

200
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,870
跟他耍耍
Let's toy with him.

201
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,390
不急 跟他耍耍
No hurry, let's toy with him!

202
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,790
算了吧！
Cut it out!

203
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,350
算了！
Cut it out!

204
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,870
算了吧！

205
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:02,270
算了算了！
Cut it out! Cut it out!

206
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:06,350
算了吧！
Cut it out...

207
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,830
算了！!
Cut it out!

208
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,950
算了！!
Cut it out!

209
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,590
算你妈的吧！
Cut the bloody hell out!

210
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:17,270
胡千
Butler!

211
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,630
是 老爷！
Yes sir!

212
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,070
多拔他几颗牙
Take him to the dentist.

213
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,910
跟我一样 全镶成金的
Fix him up with gold teeth like mine.

214
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,060
是
Yes sir!

215
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,070
夫人
Madam!

216
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,630
兄弟我此番
The reason I am here,

217
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,830
只为劫财
is to get rich,

218
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,870
不为劫色
not to get laid.

219
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,550
同床
We share a bed,

220
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,710
但不入身！
but not our dreams.

221
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,510
有枪在此
Here's a pistol.

222
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,390
若是兄弟我…
Just in case,

223
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,710
有冒犯夫人的举动
I overstep my mark,

224
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:46,750
你可以随时干掉我
shoot me between the eyes.

225
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,230
若是夫人有任何要求
But if you have that urge,

226
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,670
兄弟我…
then yours truly,

227
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,710
也决不推辞
would be happy to oblige.

228
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:00,590
睡觉
Let's sleep!

229
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:19,030
一日夫妻百日恩呐
Husband and wife - even for a day...

230
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:33,270
反正呢 我就想当县长夫人
I've always wanted to be a governor's wife,

231
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:36,990
谁是县长 我无所谓！
and I don't care who the governor is.

232
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,950
兄弟 别客气嘛
So, brother, be my guest!

233
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:40,910
我客气吗？
Your guest?

234
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:41,870
客气呀
Go ahead!

235
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:43,510
这还算客气？
You make me blush!

236
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,990
你太客气啦
Well, do I?

237
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,990
怎么才能不客气啊？
Then I must oblige.

238
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:49,670
晚了！
We're late!

239
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:50,590
前几任县长
Previous governors

240
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:52,990
把鹅城的税 收到九十年以后了
have levied tax for the next 90 years!

241
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:56,430
也就是西历二零一零年！
So everyone has paid up to 2010!

242
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:57,990
咱们来错地方了
We've come to the wrong place!

243
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:00,030
我倒是觉得这个地方不错
I like this town, though.

244
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:03,030
百姓成穷鬼了 没油水可榨了
But people here have nothing left.

245
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,660
老子从来就没想刮穷鬼的钱
I never take from the poor.

246
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,790
不刮穷鬼的钱你收谁的呀？
Who are your victims, then?

247
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,510
谁有钱赚谁的
The rich, of course.

248
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,550
当过县长吗？
Ever been a Governor?

249
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,590
没有
No.

250
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:12,980
我告诉你！
Listen carefully!

251
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:15,390
县长上任 得巧立名目
You have to devise ways to raise money,

252
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,630
拉拢豪绅 缴税捐款
Make the rich pay first,

253
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:20,590
他们交了 才能让百姓跟着交钱
townsfolk will follow suit.

254
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:23,870
得钱之后 豪绅的钱如数奉还
Then reimburse the rich with what they paid,

255
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:26,420
百姓的钱 三七分成！
and split the rest 30-70!

256
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:27,750
怎么才七成啊？
We only get 70?

257
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,590
七成是人家的！
No, the rich get 70.

258
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:32,390
能得三成还得看黄四郎的脸色
We get 30 at Huang's discretion.

259
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:33,310
谁的脸色？
At whose discretion?

260
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,580
他！
Him.

261
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:35,390
他？!
Him?

262
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,190
我大老远的来一趟
I come all this way,

263
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:40,150
就是为了看他的脸色？
only to become his running dog?

264
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,420
对！
Correct.

265
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:45,150
我好不容易劫了趟火车
It's hard enough robbing your train,

266
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,230
当了县长
and play-act governor.

267
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,740
我还得拉拢豪绅
I still have to play boot-licker to the rich,

268
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,510
还得巧立名目
make up silly excuses,

269
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,750
还得看他的脸色
and do things at his whim.

270
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,550
我不成跪着要饭的了吗？
Doesn't that make me a beggar?

271
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:55,030
那你要这么说
If you want to put it that way...

272
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,430
买官当县长还真就是跪着要饭的
Many would love to be in your position,

273
00:15:57,640 --> 00:16:00,310
就这 多少人想跪还没这门路呢！
but few could afford to buy a post.

274
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:12,310
我问问你 我为什么要上山当土匪？
Do you know why I became an outlaw?

275
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:17,230
我就是腿脚不方便 跪不下去！
It's because my legs are not built for kneeling!

276
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,710
原来你是想站着赚钱啊！
If you want to make money standing tall,

277
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,230
那还是回山里吧
ride back to the mountains.

278
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,750
这我就不明白了
I don't get this.

279
00:16:24,040 --> 00:16:25,590
我已经当了县长了
I am now governor,

280
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:27,390
怎么还不如个土匪呀？
how can I be worse off than a bandit?

281
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,270
百姓眼里 你是县长
You may be a governor to the townsfolk.

282
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,910
可是黄四郎眼里
But in the eyes of Huang,

283
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,790
你就是跪着要饭的
you're a mere beggar!

284
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:37,910
赚钱嘛 生意 不寒酸！
This is only business. There is no shame.

285
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,300
寒酸！
The hell there isn't!

286
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:40,780
很寒酸
It's shameful!

287
00:16:40,920 --> 00:16:41,950
那你是想站着？
Do you prefer to stand tall,

288
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:43,150
还是想赚钱呢？
or do you want to make money?

289
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:46,070
我是想站着 还把钱赚了
I want to do both.

290
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:46,910
赚不成！
No way.

291
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:47,630
赚不成？
Why not?

292
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,790
赚不成！
It's impossible.

293
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,910
这个能不能赚钱？
Can I make money with this?

294
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,630
能赚 山里
Yes, but only as a bandit.

295
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:56,510
这个能不能赚钱？
Or with this?

296
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,430
能赚 跪着
Yes, but only on your knees.

297
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,390
这个加上这个
Combining the two,

298
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:04,270
能不能站着把钱赚了？
can I make money standing tall?

299
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:08,110
敢问九筒大哥何方神圣？
Mr. Nine, who exactly are you?

300
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:11,150
鄙人 张麻子！
"Pocky" Zhang!

301
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:14,030
那不是树 别砍了！
Stop it! This is not a tree!

302
00:17:15,080 --> 00:17:17,230
这是冤鼓 乾隆那时候设的
It's an ancient magisterial drum!

303
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:19,550
老没人敲就生了根 长了叶
Totally neglected,

304
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:20,830
就成现在这样了
it's taken root and sprouted leaves.

305
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,110
我爹说了
Pop said to me,

306
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:24,190
有冤鼓 就说明有冤！
we need this to convene court.

307
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:25,830
他说他要判个案！
He wants to try a case.

308
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,100
哪儿有冤呐？
What case?

309
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,670
谁敢有冤呐？
Has someone filed a complaint?

310
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:29,950
这都一百多年了
It's been here for 100 years.

311
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:31,510
你要把它砍了 把鼓露出来
If you now unveil the drum,

312
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,150
不定出多大冤呐？
who knows what case it may bring?

313
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:35,390
别砍啦！你爹他人呢？
Where's your old man?

314
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,550
睡觉！
In bed.

315
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,870
跟谁睡啊？怎么还睡啊？
At this hour? Who with?

316
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,300
鼓呢？
What happened?

317
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,150
鼓呢？
Where is it going?

318
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,870
叫你别砍吧 把鼓给砍跑了
Look what you've done!

319
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:53,670
鼓鼓鼓鼓！
Drum...!

320
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:56,980
躲开
Out of my way!

321
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,430
这鼓怎么跟着我呀
It's homing in on me!

322
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:04,230
救命呀…！大人
Help! Help!

323
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:32,710
可惜了老子的酒
My wine is ruined,

324
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,870
老子的雅兴全让你给毁了
my mood destroyed!

325
00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:36,180
全毁了！
Everything's spoilt!

326
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:39,070
改日我再收拾你
I'll deal with you another day.

327
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,070
鼓都捶破了
The drum is shattered!

328
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:48,230
说明你们俩很冤呐
So there must be a case to try!

329
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,380
升堂！
Court!

330
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,950
冤从何来？
How have you been wronged?

331
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,980
没冤！
I'm not.

332
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:06,110
有冤的说冤 没冤的那就散！散会
If no one is wronged, case dismissed!

333
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:08,190
冤！
Sir!

334
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:10,710
不是我冤 是武举老爷冤！
I have wronged Master Wu.

335
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:11,860
小的不长眼
I was careless.

336
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:14,670
在躲鼓的时候碰洒了武举老爷的酒
I ran into him and knocked over his wine.

337
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:16,550
害的武举老爷没有了胃口
Completely ruining his day.

338
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:19,950
小的应该给武举老爷赔礼 赔礼
I need to kowtow and apologise. Sorry!

339
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:21,180
老子不冤
That was nothing.

340
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:22,950
敢说你不冤
How dare you say nothing?

341
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:23,870
跪下！
Kneel!

342
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:25,670
这可是黄四郎的团练教头
He coaches Huang's militia.

343
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:26,230
跪不得
Go easy on him.

344
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,990
老子是光绪三十一年
During the reign of the last Emperor,

345
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,630
皇上钦点的武举人
I was bestowed a Martial Scholar.

346
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:31,590
论官职 比你官大
My rank was higher than yours.

347
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:33,790
你应该给老子跪下
You should kneel in front of me!

348
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,150
跪下！
Kneel!

349
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,590
跪不跪？
Kneel!

350
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:39,950
还皇上！
This is bullshit!

351
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,630
哪个皇上？我见过吗？
The last Emperor? Have I ever met him?

352
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:43,990
你要是个文举人
If you'd been a Literary Scholar,

353
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,630
他应该给你磕两百个头
he'd have to kowtow 200 times.

354
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:48,430
可惜你只是个武举人
But as a Martial Scholar,

355
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:50,670
他只能给你磕一百个头
you'll get only 100 kowtows.

356
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:53,110
现在他两百个头磕完了
Since he has already done 200,

357
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,070
你还他一百个
you've to return 100 kowtows.

358
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:55,030
可我只磕了两个
But I've only kowtowed twice!

359
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,430
两个也得还你一百个
Does it really matter?

360
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,070
磕不磕？
Do it!

361
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:00,310
打！
Flog him!

362
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,950
这个不好使
That's no good.

363
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,780
得使这个！
This is more effective.

364
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:10,310
哎！别打！我磕！
Stop! I'll do it.

365
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,350
行了
Splendid!

366
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:15,790
你磕头！你数数！
You kowtow, and you do the counting.

367
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:21,910
一二三四五六…
One, two, three, four...

368
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,990
青天大老爷！
Hail, Governor!

369
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,300
起来！不准跪！
Stand up everyone!

370
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:28,670
皇上都没了 没人值得你们跪！
No one is worth kneeling to.

371
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,830
我也不值你们跪！
Least of all to me!

372
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:34,190
我来鹅城只办三件事
I've brought three things to Goose Town.

373
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,900
公平！
Justice,
justice,

374
00:20:37,080 --> 00:20:39,150
还是公平！
and goddamned justice.

375
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,390
青天大老爷！
Hail, Governor!

376
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:43,830
站起来！不准跪！
Stand up! No kneeling!

377
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,790
这就对了
That's better.

378
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:49,420
不准跪？
No kneeling?

379
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:51,230
这哪是打我的屁股
He was not only flogging me,

380
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:53,550
这明明是打您的脸
he was slapping you in the face!

381
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:59,510
老爷 等我把屁股养好了
When my butts stop hurting,

382
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,710
我亲手给你报仇！
I will personally avenge you.

383
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:03,910
那就把卖凉粉的叫来
Summon the noodle vendor.

384
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,750
县长喜欢判案
If our governor loves to try,

385
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:10,350
就安排一点案子给他判叹
we'll give him a case to try.

386
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:14,030
爹 今天你这县长干得真漂亮
Pop, you were brilliant today.

387
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,870
打武举人打得真过瘾
Flogging that martial scholar was a hoot!

388
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,590
将来我也想当县长
I'd love to be a governor one day.

389
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:21,070
你不能当县长 也不许当土匪
I don't want you to be a bandit or politician.

390
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:25,870
你爹死的时候把你交给我
When your father entrusted you to me,

391
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:29,020
我答应过他 要让你有出息
I promised I'd raise you properly.

392
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:31,950
那我当什么才有出息？
Then what should I do?

393
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:37,350
当学生！读书 多听这个
Study and learn to enjoy this.

394
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:38,900
没声啊！
There is no sound!

395
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:42,110
这帮买官的县长 就知道捞钱
Politicians only know how to bully.

396
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:43,910
唱机都撂坏了
This gramophone was broken,

397
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,750
修好了
Now it is fixed.

398
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:48,220
这单活干完了 爹赚了钱
Once we're done here,

399
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,950
我送你去留洋
I'll let you study abroad.

400
00:21:50,760 --> 00:21:51,820
东洋三年
3 years in the east,

401
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,550
西洋三年
3 in the west,

402
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:54,590
南洋三年
and 3 more in the south.

403
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:56,270
北洋 北洋三年
How about 3 years in the north?

404
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:59,830
傻孩子 你生在北洋 不必留了
No, you're born in the north.

405
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:02,390
这是谁吹的？
Who is this by?

406
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,590
听着像穆扎
I think it's Wolfgang.

407
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:10,310
他们那边叫穆扎
Sometime known as Amadeus.

408
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:12,270
咱们这边叫莫札特
We call him M-o-z-a-r-t.

409
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:15,000
你还能听出来是谁吹的呢？!
You can tell by listening?

410
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,430
得分时候
It depends.

411
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:18,110
什么时候？
On what?

412
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:21,750
那上面印着他名字的时候
If his name was printed there.

413
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:28,230
爹 这叫穆扎这人
Pop, this Mozart...

414
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:31,190
他是怎么把这东西吹到这里边的？
How did he get the sound in there?

415
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:35,420
你去留完洋 你就什么都知道了
You'll learn by studying abroad.

416
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:40,630
那这个穆扎在哪儿？
Where's this Mozart?

417
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:43,790
我留洋的时候要去哪找他？
How can I find him?

418
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:50,590
他呀 离咱们很远
He is far away from us.

419
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,830
怎么做 知道了吗？
Know what you have to do?

420
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:55,670
知道了
Yes.

421
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:58,430
谁让你去做的 你也知道了吗？
Who ordered you to do this?

422
00:22:58,760 --> 00:22:59,740
知道了
Who, sir?

423
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,790
是老爷叫你去的吗？
Did I tell you to do it?

424
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,990
是 是老爷让我去的
Yes, sir. You did.

425
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:05,830
我
No, it's "me"!

426
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:06,630
你？
You?

427
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:08,630
你 你自己
You, you yourself!

428
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,710
我自己 我自己
Yes, me and me alone.

429
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,020
听不见
I can't hear you.

430
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,230
是我自己要去的
It's my own plot.

431
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,700
没有人让我去 是我自己
There are no co-conspirators.

432
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,830
恩人！恩人！
Saviour! My saviour!

433
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,110
恩人！
Saviour!

434
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:26,510
你是叫我呢？
You're addressing me?

435
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:29,510
我什么时候成你恩人了？
Since when have I become your saviour?

436
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:32,190
不杀之恩为大恩！
You spared my life,

437
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:36,190
为报不杀之恩 我也救你一命
and I'll save yours in return.

438
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:38,510
哦？你快说
Do tell.

439
00:23:39,840 --> 00:23:42,590
寡妇 不能睡啊！
Never sleep with a widow.

440
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:45,990
必有大灾！
It's very bad luck!

441
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,150
她…
She?

442
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:54,710
真的是寡妇么？
Is she really a widow?

443
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,070
我看着不像
She doesn't act like one.

444
00:23:57,400 --> 00:24:00,030
我亲眼看见他丈夫淹死的
But I witnessed her husband drowned!

445
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:09,230
她已经成了寡妇
If she really is a widow,

446
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:12,030
我不能…
Then I must not...

447
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:14,630
让她再守活寡
Ieave her alone uncomforted.

448
00:24:21,840 --> 00:24:23,430
这是第一步
That's my first move.

449
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,710
三步之内…
Within three...

450
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,440
要不让他们滚蛋走人
they'll either leave with tails
between their legs,

451
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:29,110
要不让他们跪下当狗！
or stay and become our poodles!

452
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:32,230
对 非常对
Right, absolutely right.

453
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:35,110
老爷 您找我？
You're looking for me, sir?

454
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,790
官府的人还没来？
Have you entertained our new officials yet?

455
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:37,750
没有
Not yet.

456
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:39,060
县长不嫖妓？
The Governor doesn't frequent brothels?

457
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:42,390
不好色的县长 不一定是好县长
He'll never make a good governor.

458
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,910
我就是不好色！
I don't indulge much in sex.

459
00:24:44,080 --> 00:24:45,790
所以您当不了县长
So you won't make a good governor either.

460
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,670
我当不了县长？
Why is that so?

461
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:52,670
县长哪能跟您比呀
The two bear no comparison!

462
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,390
他只是流水的县长
Governors come and go.

463
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,590
您才是铁打的老爷
But you, sir, will always be our godfather!

464
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,910
你真会讲话
You speak well!

465
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,750
他们一定会来 你要好好记住
I'm sure they will come.

466
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:07,630
他们讲的每一句有用的话
Eavesdrop their every conversation,

467
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:10,750
都要回来跟我汇报
report their every move.

468
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,630
是
Yes.

469
00:25:11,800 --> 00:25:15,110
走吧 你不要变成小凤仙哦
Go now. Just don't become a Mata Hari!

470
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:18,750
老爷 谁是小凤仙？
Who's Mata Hari, Master?

471
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:21,950
小凤仙都不知道还当妓女
What kind of whore are you?

472
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:26,350
那可是名震京城 誉满全国的妓女
She's the world's most infamous double agent!

473
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:33,300
你们出去吧
You two can leave.

474
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:41,310
县长此刻正怀抱夫人 共枕同眠
Now the Governor is in bed with his wife.

475
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:44,790
让他睡最后一个安稳觉
Let him enjoy one more night in peace!

476
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:48,030
县长公子 以身试法
The Governor's boy is in trouble,

477
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:50,660
讲茶大堂 恭迎大驾！
your presence is requested at the teahouse.

478
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:53,140
讲茶大堂？县衙不是判案的地方吗？
Why don't they convene at the magistracy?

479
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:54,670
你这个县衙是摆设
The magistracy is just for show.

480
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:57,950
判案只有去讲茶大堂！那才是真县衙！
All cases are tried at the teahouse.

481
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,390
六爷
Master Six,

482
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,430
你吃了两碗的粉
you've eaten two bowls of jelly,

483
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,700
只给了一碗的钱
and paid only for one.

484
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,390
放屁 我就吃了一碗的粉
Bullshit! I have only eaten one bowl!

485
00:26:05,600 --> 00:26:06,990
给了他一碗的钱！
And I paid him for one.

486
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,110
他吃了几碗？
How many bowls did he eat?

487
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:09,190
两碗
Two...

488
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:10,500
不可能！
No way!

489
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:12,190
六爷是县长的儿子
Master Six is the Governor's godson,

490
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:14,070
怎么能欠你的粉钱呢？
why would he want to cheat you?

491
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:16,150
就是吃了两碗 只给了一碗的钱
But he ate two bowls and paid for one.

492
00:26:16,360 --> 00:26:20,830
县长要给我们鹅城一个公平
The Governor brings justice to our town.

493
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,110
好！
Good!

494
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:24,350
我今天讨的就是一个公平
And justice is what I seek today!

495
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:25,150
对
Hear hear!

496
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:28,750
问谁讨？问县长儿子。为什么？
From the Governor's son, of course.

497
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:32,110
他吃了两碗粉 只给了一碗的钱
Ate two bowls, paid for one!

498
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:34,230
这就叫作不公平！
That's so wrong!

499
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:36,550
既然县长儿子带头不公平
Since his boy is guilty of unjust,

500
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:38,310
那县长说的话就是个屁
the Governor's crusade is bullshit!

501
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:39,190
我操
Screw you!

502
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:42,980
六爷…
Master Six...

503
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:46,350
胡万 六爷是县长的儿子
Master Six is the Governor's godson!

504
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:47,950
怎么会欠他的粉钱呢？
Would he cheat over a bowl of jelly?

505
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:49,910
你亲眼看见了？
Did you see it with your own eyes?

506
00:26:50,080 --> 00:26:53,390
嘿 你个吃里爬外的东西
You double-crosser!

507
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:54,750
怎么着？
What's wrong with you?

508
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,190
屁股不疼了？
You're thinking with your butts?

509
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:59,030
今不聊屁股的事
It's not about my butts.

510
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:00,630
就聊凉粉
We're here for the truth!

511
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:03,390
一碗就是一碗 两碗就是两碗
One or two bowls?

512
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:04,620
不能含糊
No beating about the bush!

513
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:07,390
六爷 汉子！佩服！
I admire your courage, sir.

514
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,790
一就是一 二就是二
I know how to count!

515
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,070
我今天就吃了一碗凉粉
I ate only one bowl!

516
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:16,750
你给了一碗的钱 吃了两碗粉
You ate two and paid for one.

517
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:19,750
你没钱是吧 我帮你给！
If you can't afford it, my treat!

518
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:23,070
看见了吗？多少碗我都付得起！
I can afford all the jelly in this world!

519
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:25,510
但是吃一碗的粉 就给一碗的钱
But I pay only for what I ate.

520
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:28,950
这么多钱 他吃了多少碗粉啊
How many bowls did he eat?

521
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:30,750
你早说不就得了吗
Let's be frank.

522
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,900
他要个公平
He wants to be treated fairly.

523
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:34,350
你不是欺负老实人吗？
It's wrong to bully a commoner.

524
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:46,180
告诉我 你是老实人吗？
Are you an honest person?

525
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:46,950
我是
Yes, I am...

526
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:49,270
那你就说实话 我到底吃了几碗粉？
How many bowls did I eat?

527
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,910
你告诉他！
Tell him!

528
00:27:51,280 --> 00:27:52,550
你说不说？
Speak up!

529
00:27:53,080 --> 00:27:56,950
拿枪吓唬一可怜的 卖凉粉的
Stop threatening this poor man with a gun!

530
00:27:57,120 --> 00:28:00,150
有枪是吧？谁没有枪啊！
Who doesn't carry a gun around here?

531
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:02,550
孙守义
Noodle vendor!

532
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:05,630
大声说 他吃了几碗
How many bowls did he eat?

533
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:11,750
守义 在座所有的乡亲
Everyone in this teahouse,

534
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:15,270
都会为你和你的家人作主的
will bear witness on your behalf.

535
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:18,230
大声说 几碗
Speak up! How many?

536
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:26,260
两碗
Two bowls.

537
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,870
你是一个恶人！
You're nasty!

538
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:39,950
比恶是吧 我比你还恶
But I dare you to match me!

539
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,510
都看好了啊
Take a good look!

540
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,910
今我肚子里要有两碗粉
If there are two bowls of jelly in me,

541
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,030
我白死
I'll die!

542
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:51,310
你要是肚子里只有一碗粉
If there's only one,

543
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:53,230
我死！
I'll die.

544
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:58,670
要是有两碗粉 我陪六爷一起死
If he has two bowls in him, I'll die with him!

545
00:28:59,040 --> 00:29:00,550
凉粉呢？
Where's the jelly?

546
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:05,310
太浅了 我看不见
Deeper! I can't see.

547
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:10,870
六爷！佩服！
Very gutsy, sir!

548
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:14,150
凉粉在肠子里 你得横着拉一下
Try sliding the blade sideway,

549
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:15,300
才能让我看得见
so that we can all see.

550
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:18,190
六爷 让大家看看是一碗还是两碗
Show us if there is one or two bowls.

551
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:19,750
拉！
Out with it!

552
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:25,710
六爷 碗！
Here's a bowl, sir.

553
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:39,590
看见了吧！看见了吧！
See! Can you see?

554
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:42,870
是不是只有一碗！
One bowl!
There's only one bowl, right?

555
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:46,270
六爷 挺住！我去给你请大夫！
Hang in there! I'll get a doctor!

556
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:50,590
别走！是不是只有一碗！
There's only one bowl, right?

557
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:53,910
是不是只有一碗！是不是！
There's only one bowl, right?

558
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,140
该你了
Your turn!

559
00:30:02,600 --> 00:30:04,510
我知道你只吃了一碗
I knew it all along.

560
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,150
你上当了
You fell for it.

561
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:11,670
不能杀…！我不能放！
You mustn't kill him! No, I won't!

562
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:12,950
为什么不能杀？
Tell me why I should spare him,

563
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,750
说不出说法来 我把你一起杀了
or I'll shoot you, too.

564
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:16,830
杀了他 六子白死
Don't let Six die in vain!

565
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:19,630
我没有杀他 他自己捅自己的！
I didn't do it. He stabbed himself.

566
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:20,750
我们在打赌
We'd a wager.

567
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:21,900
他输了
He lost.

568
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,630
大哥 你让我一枪崩了他！
Let me blast his head off!

569
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:25,750
你不敢杀我！你不能杀我！
You wouldn't dare! You can't do it.

570
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,870
黄四郎就想看你这样！
Huang is provoking you.

571
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,230
一脸的败相！
He wants you to lose your head.

572
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,190
杀了他就是输 不杀还能赢
We'll lose if we kill him now.

573
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:32,070
放人
Let him go.

574
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:34,750
杀人诛心 杀人诛心！
You must destroy Huang's soul!

575
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,550
师爷说得对放人
- Pop, he's right. - Let him go!

576
00:30:43,520 --> 00:30:48,110
刀进了肚子 那凉粉还是凉粉？
He stabbed himself? What about the jelly?

577
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:49,310
是
Yes

578
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:50,510
不是
and no...

579
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:53,710
我就想知道 凉粉到底还是不是凉粉
Tell me if it was still jelly.

580
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,550
是凉粉！
Yes, it was.

581
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:56,070
过来过来
Come over here.

582
00:30:57,520 --> 00:30:58,660
那么…
And...

583
00:30:58,960 --> 00:30:59,940
人死了？
is he dead?

584
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,510
死了
Yes.

585
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,820
所以…你就把我供出来了？
Did you implicate me?

586
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:07,790
我是用老爷的名字吓唬他们
I did invoke your name.

587
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,180
他们被吓着了么？
Were they scared?

588
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:11,790
他们说杀人诛心！
They said to kill, a person's soul
must first be destroyed.

589
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:15,270
杀人还要诛心？
Murder? Soul destruction?

590
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:18,150
好可怕啊！
How awful.

591
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:24,790
六弟 四哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I vow to avenge you!

592
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:34,350
六弟 五哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I swear I'll avenge you!

593
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,300
六哥 七弟发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I vow to avenge you!

594
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:44,980
二哥喝醉了 他让我带话
Two is drunk. I am pledging for him.

595
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,910
二哥发誓替你报仇！
He will avenge your death, too.

596
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:56,310
六弟 三哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I swear to avenge you!

597
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,790
二哥没喝醉 他生气了！
Two is sober, he's just pissed off!

598
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,750
大哥不想让大伙拼命
Chief doesn't want to risk our lives.

599
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,910
命都不拼 还算麻匪吗？
Are we boy scouts or what?

600
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:05,190
大哥不应该听他的
Chief should have ignored Tang.

601
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:07,350
姓汤的不是个好玩意
He is a good-for-nothing!

602
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:17,630
六爷 黄四郎这招叫杀人不用刀
Huang kills without lifting a finger!

603
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:20,710
我给你爹出的招叫杀人诛心
We must retaliate by destroying his soul.

604
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:24,350
不能拼命啊！拼命还怎么赚钱！
We can't jeopardise our chance to get rich!

605
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,980
六子
Six...

606
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:37,870
挣钱对我算个事儿吗？
I do not care about being rich.

607
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,870
我不是要杀人诛心 是没想出好办法
But I must come up with a game plan

608
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:43,990
我要把黄四郎连根都拔掉
to rid of Huang once and for all

609
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,230
给我点时间
Give me time,

610
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:50,670
六子 爹发誓一定给你报仇！
Pop will avenge your death.

611
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,790
把脸收拾收拾
Show your respect!

612
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:00,070
六爷 一路走好
Have a safe journey, Six.

613
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:03,550
六爷 一路走好！
Safe travel, Six!

614
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:09,910
先打哪一张牌？
How should I play my hand?

615
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:15,070
请客、斩首、收下当狗！
Banquet, kill him or throw him to the dogs?

616
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:15,910
斩！
I'd say kill him!

617
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:16,910
NO！
No!

618
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,140
NO？
No?

619
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:20,110
请客！
Host a banquet!

620
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:22,510
鸿门宴！凶多吉少
Dinner invitation! It's a death trap!

621
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:24,950
杀人诛心 赫然奏效！
Our ploy is working!

622
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:26,390
我再送你一个字
I have another idea: delay tactics.

623
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,790
抻！抻拉得越久 赚得越多
The longer we drag this on the better!

624
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:31,030
到时候跪在这儿的就是黄四郎本人
Huang will end up kneeling here.

625
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,550
什么鸿门宴！
What kind of banquet is this?

626
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,310
就是恶霸请土匪！
It's just a meeting between two thugs!

627
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:36,110
项羽请刘邦啊！
It's like MacBeth hosting Banquo.

628
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,550
刘邦后来干什么去了？
What'd become of Banquo the guest?

629
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:38,310
当皇帝了
His son became king.

630
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,660
项羽呢？
And MacBeth the host?

631
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:43,230
那 赴宴？
So we should go.

632
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:48,270
赴宴！正好借机把黄四郎也笼络过来
We can also sound out Huang,

633
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:50,510
咱们三个联手一起捞钱
and see if we can work together.

634
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,430
「把家伙拿来」
"Bring the guns."

635
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,950
「换上黄家衣服跟我走」
"Dress up as Huang's militia and follow me."

636
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:57,950
明白
Got it!

637
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:59,550
「干掉黄四郎 给六子报仇」
"Kill Huang and avenge Six!"

638
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:01,070
明白
Understood!

639
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:06,070
老汤 你是把六子的死当捞钱的成本了？
You see Six's death as a shortcut to bonanza?

640
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:09,430
我看你当成本 赚的钱会更多
Perhaps your severed head can make us more.

641
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:10,790
这是什么意思？
What do you mean?

642
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:13,990
走！去会会你的新朋友
Let's go and meet your new pal.

643
00:34:14,160 --> 00:34:15,550
立正！
Attention!

644
00:34:38,720 --> 00:34:43,660
县长 师爷 大驾光临！有失远迎！
Governor, counselor! Welcome!

645
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:46,950
黄老爷的宅邸 竹林掩映 碉楼耸立
Master's citadel dominates Goose Town.

646
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:49,710
易守难攻 万夫莫开！
It is simply impregnable.

647
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:53,150
县长英雄气概 师爷文采斐然
An intrepid governor, an erudite counselor.

648
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:55,590
珠联璧合！二位请！
What a dream team!

649
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:01,710
六爷的死 壮烈！
Master Six has died heroically.

650
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:04,070
今天请县长来
I've invited you here today

651
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:08,590
就是要当面为六爷讨回这个公道！
to witness how justice is done.

652
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,630
如果真的是黄某指使
If I'm proven to be the instigator,

653
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,020
那我就像六爷一样
I will follow Master Six's footstep,

654
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:14,030
当众剖腹自杀！
and disembowel myself!

655
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:16,950
不但自杀 还请县长您
I invite you to be my second,

656
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:19,270
当我的介错人
to ritualistically cut my head off

657
00:35:19,640 --> 00:35:23,590
砍下我人头 高挂艳阳楼顶！
and hang it from the restaurant.

658
00:35:28,200 --> 00:35:29,310
万一不是我
If I'm proven innocent,

659
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:32,670
那就是辱我名声
those who slandered me

660
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:34,710
欺骗县长
and shamed you in the process...

661
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,430
你们自裁
will have to kill themselves.

662
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:40,990
要么三命抵一命 要么随时告发我
It's me against these three.

663
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:42,990
我随时死
I am ready.

664
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:52,750
黄老爷 我听说自裁用短刀
You should use this for disembowelment.

665
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,590
长刀归介错人
The full blade is for your second.

666
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,790
是吗？
Really?

667
00:35:58,240 --> 00:36:03,590
果然在行！县长随时可以当我的介错人
It's great to have an expert as my second!

668
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:07,510
马县长 请！
This way, please.

669
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:10,060
马某人这个县长 买来的
I bought this governorship.

670
00:36:10,240 --> 00:36:11,750
买官就是为了挣钱
Sole purpose is to get rich.

671
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:15,390
而且 马某人不喜欢挣穷人的钱
But I don't take from the poor.

672
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:17,270
那你想挣谁的钱呢？
Then who are you targeting?

673
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:19,350
谁有钱就挣谁的！
Only the wealthy people.

674
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:20,310
那谁有钱？
Who are the wealthy?

675
00:36:20,520 --> 00:36:21,790
你有钱
Such as you.

676
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:27,430
爽快！县长看上什么了 随便拿
Whatever you fancy, help yourself.

677
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:34,030
我不是土匪！我是县长
I'm no bandit. I'm a governor.

678
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:37,950
县长挣钱得讲究个名正言顺才是
I make my fortune the proper way.

679
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:38,870
说得好
Well said!

680
00:36:39,240 --> 00:36:40,990
我们鹅城有两大家族
Goose Town has two big families.

681
00:36:41,160 --> 00:36:44,070
都是把人卖到America修铁路
They sell people to America to build railroads,

682
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:46,800
挣的都是dollar
in return for dollars!

683
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,350
还说刀的事
What do you mean by dolls?

684
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:52,180
NO… dollar  美国人用的钱
No, d-o-l-l-a-r-s! American money.

685
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:53,420
dollar！You know？
Dollar! You know?

686
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,990
dollar 到了
Oh, dollars!

687
00:36:55,160 --> 00:36:58,910
黄老爷一来 钱就到了
I can smell it in your presence!

688
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:02,300
-喝一杯吧       -好 来
- Let's drink to that! - Great, cheers!

689
00:37:02,520 --> 00:37:03,870
来…
Cheers!

690
00:37:06,160 --> 00:37:08,990
黄老爷 客气了
Master Huang is so modest.

691
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:11,230
整个南国谁不知道
It is an open secret that,

692
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:12,660
在鹅城
in Goose Town,

693
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:14,710
你黄四郎是老大！
Master Huang is our real boss!

694
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:17,750
老大往往是空架子
It is hard to be a boss.

695
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:21,510
每天眼一睁 几百人吃、喝、拉、撒
Hundreds of people everyday

696
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:23,150
都要等着我伺候
waiting to be fed.

697
00:37:23,320 --> 00:37:25,670
真正落到我嘴里的 能有几口
There is little left for me.

698
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:29,510
如果县长真的急着赚钱
If you're looking to make a fast buck,

699
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:31,830
我倒是有个好去处！
I know exactly what to do.

700
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,070
哦？请讲！
Please tell.

701
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:37,520
张麻子
Pocky Zhang!

702
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:45,550
真死了！
One of them just died!

703
00:38:00,200 --> 00:38:01,550
张麻子？
Pocky Zhang?

704
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:03,870
对 张麻子！
Yes, Pocky Zhang!

705
00:38:04,080 --> 00:38:07,910
那么这个张麻子 是跟我们有关系呢？
What has he got to do with us?

706
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:09,990
还是跟钱有关系？
Or with our money?

707
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:11,140
都有关系！
Everything!

708
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:13,350
莫非他在鹅城？
Is he here in Goose Town?

709
00:38:13,560 --> 00:38:14,700
在…
Well, yes...

710
00:38:16,640 --> 00:38:18,030
也不在！
and no!

711
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:26,310
黄老爷这话 还挺有玄机啊！
Master Huang speaks in riddles!

712
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:30,750
这小子到底在哪呢？
Where is he, then?

713
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:33,510
听黄爷给咱们聊聊
Let Master Huang enlightens us.

714
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:36,670
此人盘踞鹅城周边交通咽喉
He has grabbed Goose Town by its balls!

715
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:37,900
-明白吗？     -不明白
- Know what I mean? - No

716
00:38:38,120 --> 00:38:39,750
我是做什么生意的？明白吗？
Know what I do for a living?

717
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:40,590
不明白
No.

718
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,670
小半个民国的烟土
Half the opium smokers in this nation

719
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,630
都是黄老爷您在贩卖
rely on Master Huang for their supply!

720
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:48,750
错！我不过是给刘都统当跑腿的
No, I'm only a pawn for General Liu.

721
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:51,150
而且只是其中一条腿
I'm just one of his runners!

722
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:53,430
那么刘都统到底有几条腿呢？
How many runners does Liu have?

723
00:38:53,640 --> 00:38:55,110
三条呗
Three.

724
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:57,350
黄老爷还是条大腿
And Master is the most able one!

725
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:59,270
对！大腿！
Yes, the strongest one!

726
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:00,870
可是我这条腿…
But this runner,

727
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:02,150
断了！
is now crippled!

728
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:03,110
断了？
Crippled?

729
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:03,830
怎么断的？
What happened?

730
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:07,230
我的货十回有八回被张麻子劫走了！
Zhang has seized nearly all my goods.

731
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:09,830
你想想 他赚了多少钱？
Imagine what he can make from them.

732
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,070
那这个张麻子很富有啊！
He must be very well off!

733
00:39:12,240 --> 00:39:13,630
还有这种事儿？
I wonder if this is true.

734
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:16,710
如果你们可以去剿匪的话
You can write your own cheque,

735
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:19,390
钱要多少有多少
if you can take him out!

736
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,430
我们没胆子剿匪
We wouldn't dare to!

737
00:39:21,680 --> 00:39:24,190
但是 借剿匪之名敛财的胆子
But if this can make us rich,

738
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:26,430
还是有 而且很大！
I wouldn't mind having a go!

739
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:31,790
那就不要怪我！就怪你们没出息
Then blame yourself for your timidity!

740
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:34,750
不过 我还可以帮你们一个忙
But I would be happy to assist.

741
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:36,990
我出钱 当诱饵
I can put up money as a bait.

742
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:40,940
我出多少 两大家族必须出多少！
The families have to match my contribution.

743
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:43,680
就等您这句话呢！足够！
We're hoping you'd say that.

744
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,190
那您出八十万？
How about $800,000?

745
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:48,150
NO！我出一百八十万
No! I'll put up $1.8 million!

746
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,190
出得多 挣得多！
The more the merrier!

747
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:55,030
明白！事成之后 一百八十万如数奉还
Yes, we'll pay you back $1.8 million,

748
00:39:55,200 --> 00:39:59,070
咱们分两大家族那点儿dollar！
and split the dollars from the others.

749
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,830
一百八十万不用还！
There's no need to pay him back!

750
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:03,790
不就是剿匪么！剿！
We'll hit these bandits hard!

751
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:06,190
咱们把张麻子劫走的那点钱
Whatever they seized in the past,

752
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,550
全拿回来 还给黄老爷！
we will retrieve for the Master.

753
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:10,230
到那个时候
Look at the bigger picture,

754
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:13,710
这一百八十万就是九牛身上的一根毛
the $1.8 million bounty is but a strand of hair.

755
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:14,710
您还在意吗？
Surely you won't mind!

756
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:17,910
不就是个小小的张麻子吗？办他！
We'll get rid of Pocky Zhang!

757
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:18,830
硬！
Cool!

758
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:19,980
-硬吗？     -够硬！
- Cool enough? - Very cool!

759
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:21,510
硬不硬以后再说！
We can discuss that later.

760
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:23,350
我脑子里想的只有一件事
The only thing I want to do now

761
00:40:23,560 --> 00:40:26,350
替黄老爷把这条腿接上！
is to fix Master's crippled leg.

762
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:29,030
一个张麻子也太嚣张了！
Pocky Zhang's such a nuisance.

763
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:31,870
欺负到黄哥头上了 不答应
He shouldn't have messed with Master Huang!

764
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:32,750
喝酒
Let's top up.

765
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:37,670
我以为 酒一口一口喝
I believe in taking our time,

766
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,270
路一步一步走
doing things step by step!

767
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,070
步子迈大了 喀！
I don't want to break my balls

768
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,270
容易扯着蛋
by over-stretching!

769
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:44,510
应该先把dollar分清楚
We should agree on the split first,

770
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:45,870
