My citadel is impregnable.

797
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:51,510
易守难攻 他进不来！
There's no way that he can get in.

798
00:41:51,680 --> 00:41:53,710
那你怎么就真的相信
Are you sure

799
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:56,950
只有我跟师爷进了你的碉楼呢？
that we're the only ones here?

800
