撤
Let's split.

803
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:12,950
「遵命 但我很担心你」
"Chief, watch your back."

804
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:14,150
听见了吧？
Did you hear that?

805
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,110
