824
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:14,030
嘘！quite quite！
Quiet, quiet...

825
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:16,390
那么彼时彼刻
So it was there and then...

826
00:43:16,600 --> 00:43:21,390
恰如此时此刻
A bit like, here and now!

827
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:26,670
