这孩子将来最大的缺点
He said my Achilles heel

838
00:43:47,800 --> 00:43:49,550
就是不会装糊涂！
would be my inability to play act!

839
00:43:49,720 --> 00:43:51,350
大哥 我还能改吗？
Can I change it?

840
00:43:51,560 --> 00:43:53,310
改不了！天生的
No way! It's in your genes!

841
