I'll send over $1.8 million now.

854
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:29,910
无功不受禄 现在收钱太早
That's too soon. We haven't started yet!

855
00:44:30,080 --> 00:44:31,430
黛玉 晴雯！
Marie, Claire!

856
