We'll run for our lives!

865
00:44:52,800 --> 00:44:55,630
有道是 江湖本无路
Roads won't exist in this world of chaos,

866
00:44:55,800 --> 00:44:58,630
有了腿 便有了路！
unless people like us run on them!

867
00:44:59,600 --> 00:45:02,230
明白 明白
I see, I see...

868
00:45:02,400 --> 00:45:03,750
我也明白
Yes, me too.

869
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:07,110
该死的东西！
Stupid bitch!

870
00:45:13,000 --> 00:45:15,190
花有重开日
While flowers can blossom again,

871
00:45:15,360 --> 00:45:17,430
人无再少年
time lost will never return.

872
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:19,990
姑娘如花似玉
This girl is as delicate as jade.

873
00:45:20,160 --> 00:45:22,540
大哥 怒不得啊！
Please don't be mad at her.

874
00:45:23,520 --> 00:45:25,550
黄老爷 easy easy！
Master Huang, easy easy...

875
00:45:37,520 --> 00:45:38,910
相见恨晚！
Shame we didn't meet until now!

876
00:45:39,080 --> 00:45:41,150
姑娘、钻石一并送上！
Diamonds, the girl - they're all yours.

877
00:45:41,320 --> 00:45:43,310
唉！我带夫人来的
I've brought my wife with me.

878
00:45:43,520 --> 00:45:44,990
再收姑娘不方便
So I can't take her home.

879
00:45:45,160 --> 00:45:46,510
那钻石送夫人
Then take the diamonds for your wife.

880
00:45:46,680 --> 00:45:48,350
好！我先替她收着
I accept them on her behalf.

881
00:45:49,640 --> 00:45:50,670
起来吧
Get up.

882
00:45:51,920 --> 00:45:54,870
不是黛玉和晴雯吗？
I thought you'd summoned two girls.

883
00:45:55,040 --> 00:45:57,070
