How come there's only her?

884
00:45:57,240 --> 00:45:59,870
莫非她就叫黛玉晴雯？
You mean she is Marie-Claire?

885
00:46:00,040 --> 00:46:01,350
说你不会装糊涂吧
You are really naive!

886
00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:03,190
起了个东洋名字
She's adopted a fashionable name.

887
00:46:03,360 --> 00:46:06,430
黛玉晴雯子！
It's Marie-Claire!

888
00:46:08,320 --> 00:46:10,150
全死了！
There goes the last of them!

889
00:46:10,320 --> 00:46:11,870
师爷 高！
A wise counselor!

890
00:46:12,640 --> 00:46:14,230
县长 硬！
A tough governor!

891
00:46:14,520 --> 00:46:17,080
黄老爷又高又硬！
Master, you're both wise and tough.

892
00:46:17,840 --> 00:46:19,990
你到底是不是张麻子？
Are you really "Pocky" Zhang?

893
00:46:21,240 --> 00:46:22,790
要说你是吧
Supposing that you are.

894
00:46:23,800 --> 00:46:25,390
掰断刘都统大腿
You've already made a fortune

895
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:26,820
挣那么多钱
from "crippling" Liu's runners.

896
00:46:27,160 --> 00:46:30,310
何苦进城当县长呢？
Why bother with Goose Town?

897
00:46:32,320 --> 00:46:34,700
要说你不是吧…
But if you are someone else...

898
00:46:36,240 --> 00:46:37,550
恩人？
Saviour?

899
00:46:55,640 --> 00:46:57,910
今晚 杀鸡取卵！
Kill the chicken and take the eggs.

900
00:46:58,080 --> 00:47:00,350
一定要在县长的床上
Let him die in his own bed.

901
00:47:01,200 --> 00:47:03,950
不要让人以为吃了我的饭
Don't kill him on his way home

902
00:47:04,120 --> 00:47:07,030
