after dining as my guest.

903
00:47:07,200 --> 00:47:08,110
明白！
Understood!

904
00:47:08,280 --> 00:47:09,070
哪个是鸡？
Who is the "chicken"?

905
00:47:09,240 --> 00:47:09,870
县长！
The Governor.

906
00:47:10,040 --> 00:47:10,790
