My pleasure, sir.

914
00:47:26,760 --> 00:47:29,430
明白不明白 为什么派你去？
Know why I'm sending you?

915
00:47:29,640 --> 00:47:30,350
因为我死了
It's because I'm already dead.

916
00:47:30,560 --> 00:47:31,390
为什么你会死呢？
Do you know why?

917
00:47:31,600 --> 00:47:32,820
因为我把老爷给供出来了
I shouldn't have implicated you.

918
00:47:33,000 --> 00:47:37,390
对喽！如果你活着 早晚都会死
Right! If you are alive, you'll eventually die.

919
