But I've changed my mind.

964
00:49:38,320 --> 00:49:40,950
鱼死网破报不了仇
I can't take revenge this way.

965
00:49:42,160 --> 00:49:44,390
弟兄们不能再死人了
I can't risk more lives.

966
00:49:44,600 --> 00:49:46,310
大哥 你怎么在这儿啊？
Chief, we're looking for you.

967
00:49:46,520 --> 00:49:47,790
你怎么让我们撤了呀？
Why did you signal retreat?

968
00:49:47,960 --> 00:49:49,790
黄四郎听见你们吹的哨声
Huang heard your whistling.

969
00:49:49,920 --> 00:49:51,750
我就绝对安全了
I knew that I was safe.

970
00:49:52,200 --> 00:49:55,110
去吧 我跟六子单独待会儿
Leave, I want to spend time alone with Six.

971
00:49:57,400 --> 00:49:58,710
今天我算明白了
It has finally dawned on me,

972
00:49:59,880 --> 00:50:03,030
为什么当初我会上山当麻匪
why I became a bandit in the first place.

973
00:50:03,600 --> 00:50:06,060
就是因为跟这帮东西玩不起
I was no match for these people.

974
00:50:06,400 --> 00:50:09,510
现在为了你 我必须玩得起
But I must take them on at their own game now,

975
00:50:10,640 --> 00:50:11,830
还得玩得赢
and to win for you.

976
00:50:19,680 --> 00:50:20,510
谁？
What the heck?

977
00:50:23,640 --> 00:50:26,390
偷我的钻石！
You stole my diamonds.

978
00:50:27,280 --> 00:50:28,710
这石头是给你的吗？
They're not meant for you.

979
00:50:28,880 --> 00:50:30,950
是给县长夫人的
They're a gift for Mrs. Governor!

980
00:50:31,120 --> 00:50:33,630
咱们俩谁是县长？
Which of us is the Governor?

981
00:50:36,720 --> 00:50:37,940
谁是县长？
Who's the Governor?

982
00:50:39,160 --> 00:50:42,430
我问你呢 谁是县长？
Tell me who's the Governor!

983
00:50:42,640 --> 00:50:44,310
你是要杀我？
You want to kill me?

984
00:50:44,640 --> 00:50:45,950
还是要睡我？
Or to sleep with me?

985
00:50:47,600 --> 00:50:48,710
有什么不一样吗？
Is there a difference?

986
00:50:48,880 --> 00:50:49,990
不一样啊！
It's different!

987
00:50:50,160 --> 00:50:52,310
那就先睡 再杀
I can bed you first, and kill you later.

988
00:50:53,080 --> 00:50:54,430
那还是杀了我吧
Then you'd better kill me now.

989
00:50:54,680 --> 00:50:56,750
杀了你 我还怎么睡啊
I don't sleep with dead bodies!

990
00:51:02,760 --> 00:51:07,150
我不能酒后欺负一个寡妇
I won't take drunken advantage of a widow,

991
00:51:08,120 --> 00:51:09,870
是跟你睡
so I'll just sleep next to you,

992
00:51:10,880 --> 00:51:12,830
不是睡你
not with you!

993
00:52:00,360 --> 00:52:02,030
我居然上了你们的当！
Holy smoke! I was fooled!

994
00:52:02,200 --> 00:52:04,070
你和武举人都是假死 是吧？
You and Wu both faked death!

995
00:52:04,240 --> 00:52:04,990
不错
That's right.

996
00:52:05,160 --> 00:52:05,950
为什么冒充麻匪？
Why dressed up as a bandit?

997
00:52:06,120 --> 00:52:08,420
老子就是麻匪 张麻子是我大哥
I'm a bandit. "Pocky" Zhang's my boss!

998
00:52:08,640 --> 00:52:10,190
那你是老几呀？
What's your rank, then?

999
00:52:10,360 --> 00:52:11,030
老三
I am Three!

1000
00:52:11,200 --> 00:52:12,750
老三 你出名了
Three, you've hit big time!

1001
00:52:12,920 --> 00:52:13,710
有人冒充你了！
You've got yourself a fake!

1002
00:52:13,880 --> 00:52:15,670
别听他废话了 大哥
Chief, don't listen to his bullshit!

1003
00:52:15,840 --> 00:52:17,030
六子就死在他手上
He plotted Six's death.

1004
00:52:17,200 --> 00:52:18,110
你让我一枪崩了他
Let me shoot him now!

1005
00:52:18,280 --> 00:52:18,910
大哥？
Chief?

1006
00:52:19,080 --> 00:52:20,710
是你大哥张麻子派你来的
Were you sent by "Pocky" Zhang?

1007
00:52:20,880 --> 00:52:22,390
还是你老爷黄四郎派你来的？
Or by Master Huang?

1008
00:52:22,600 --> 00:52:23,740
不能说错啊！
I want the right answer!

1009
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:26,670
-黄老爷     -为什么？
- Master Huang. - Why?

1010
00:52:26,840 --> 00:52:28,950
他让我们假扮麻匪在城里抢劫
We commit crimes posing as bandits,

1011
00:52:29,400 --> 00:52:30,910
他逼县长下令剿匪
forcing governors to launch expeditions.

1012
00:52:31,080 --> 00:52:32,590
骗豪绅 刮百姓
Creating more chances for Huang to swindle.

1013
00:52:32,760 --> 00:52:33,350
然后呢？
And then?

1014
00:52:33,560 --> 00:52:34,230
-没了     -没了？
- That's all. - Really?

1015
00:52:34,400 --> 00:52:35,380
其他事我真不知道！
I don't know anything else!

1016
00:52:35,600 --> 00:52:37,030
为什么朝我床上开枪？
Why did you target my bed?

1017
00:52:37,200 --> 00:52:39,760
黄老爷说你霸气外露
Master said you're arrogant,

1018
00:52:39,960 --> 00:52:40,940
危险！
a threat!

1019
00:52:41,640 --> 00:52:43,550
回去给他带个话 告诉他
Take him a message:

1020
00:52:43,720 --> 00:52:45,750
他喜欢让人假死这一套
While he likes people to fake death,

1021
00:52:45,920 --> 00:52:49,350
正好 我也喜欢让人多死几回这一套
I'm fond of killing people more than once!

1022
00:52:49,560 --> 00:52:50,750
您要放我回去？
Letting me off again?

1023
00:52:50,960 --> 00:52:52,390
只有你的话他听得懂
He can only understand words you say.

1024
00:52:52,600 --> 00:52:53,870
大哥 可您到底是？
Chief, you're...

1025
00:52:54,040 --> 00:52:55,670
不错 张麻子！
Yes, "Pocky" Zhang.

1026
00:52:55,880 --> 00:52:57,190
可大哥您脸上没麻子
Where are your pockmarks?

1027
00:52:57,360 --> 00:52:58,910
黄四郎脸上有四吗？
Does your boss have "Huang"
inscribed on his face?

1028
00:53:00,560 --> 00:53:01,310
懂了
That's true.

1029
00:53:01,520 --> 00:53:02,790
兄弟
My friend,

1030
00:53:03,640 --> 00:53:05,070
我是张麻子这件事
you must not tell anyone,

1031
00:53:05,240 --> 00:53:06,910
要替我永远保密
that I am "Pocky" Zhang.

1032
00:53:07,080 --> 00:53:07,750
永远保密！
You have my word!

1033
00:53:07,920 --> 00:53:11,030
我说我当不了县长
I never want to be a governor,

1034
00:53:11,240 --> 00:53:15,830
你非花钱让我买这个官
but you still bought me this post!

1035
00:53:17,560 --> 00:53:21,180
现在官被人家抢走了
The position has been usurped,

1036
00:53:21,680 --> 00:53:25,790
你也就这么死了！
and now you're dead too.

1037
00:53:26,880 --> 00:53:27,990
黄四郎带人来了
Huang has brought his militia.

1038
00:53:28,160 --> 00:53:29,590
说是要帮我们打麻匪
Wanting to fight bandits with us.

1039
00:53:29,760 --> 00:53:31,110
她是我老婆！
She was my wife.

1040
00:53:31,280 --> 00:53:33,150
-我是县长！     -让他进来
- I am the governor! - Let him in.

1041
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:35,880
我就是马邦德！
I am Ma Bangde!

1042
00:53:38,920 --> 00:53:41,380
县长如何了？县长如何了？
Is the Governor okay?

1043
00:53:41,600 --> 00:53:43,830
你们追！一个麻匪也不能跑！
Give chase! Don't let anyone get away.

1044
00:53:48,720 --> 00:53:50,670
天杀的麻匪
Those goddamned bandits!

1045
00:53:50,840 --> 00:53:52,710
伤天害理
Scum of the earth!

1046
00:53:53,040 --> 00:53:57,030
县长刚刚上任 竟和他的夫人双双…
The Governor has only just arrived...

1047
00:54:02,040 --> 00:54:04,710
我说我当不了这个县长！
Said I didn't want to be a governor,

1048
00:54:04,880 --> 00:54:08,990
你非得给我花钱买这个官！
but you still bought me this post!

1049
00:54:10,160 --> 00:54:13,430
现在官倒是到手了
The governership is now mine,

1050
00:54:14,600 --> 00:54:17,670
你倒这么走了！
but you've left me on my own.

1051
00:54:20,440 --> 00:54:21,990
她是我老婆！
She was my wife.

1052
00:54:22,800 --> 00:54:24,070
我就是县长
I am the governor!

1053
00:54:24,240 --> 00:54:26,430
我就是马邦德！
I am Ma Bangde!

1054
00:54:27,000 --> 00:54:30,190
你呀 太年轻了
You're too hot-headed.

1055
00:54:30,640 --> 00:54:33,350
不该一进城就枪毙麻匪
You shouldn't have shot those bandits.

1056
00:54:33,600 --> 00:54:36,830
他们一定会报复你的
They'll take revenge for sure.

1057
00:54:37,680 --> 00:54:39,710
不哭 不哭
Don't cry.

1058
00:54:39,880 --> 00:54:42,070
她是为鹅城死的
She died for Goose Town.

1059
00:54:42,400 --> 00:54:44,910
得厚葬她呀
She deserves a proper burial!

1060
00:54:46,960 --> 00:54:50,070
得让所有的乡绅都过来
Invite every townsfolk to attend.

1061
00:54:50,200 --> 00:54:53,590
都来都来 我会安排
Certainly. I'll take care of it.

1062
00:54:59,400 --> 00:55:04,260
因为天父依照他的恩赐和美意
"Here lies Madam Governor"

1063
00:55:04,960 --> 00:55:10,080
容我们这位姐妹 容我们这位兄弟
"Master Six rests here in peace"

1064
00:55:10,280 --> 00:55:13,150
…放下今生的担子
...to be relieved of life's burden.

1065
00:55:13,360 --> 00:55:17,390
我们就亲切的将他放入土中
Thus we commit their bodies to earth.

1066
00:55:18,120 --> 00:55:20,390
他们本是尘土
From which they came,

1067
00:55:20,800 --> 00:55:24,750
现在 他们依然是尘土
and do now return.

1068
00:55:24,960 --> 00:55:28,950
我们知道 这一切的生命气息
We know we can place ourselves,

1069
00:55:29,120 --> 00:55:33,550
都在永生的慈爱的天父手里
in the hands of our Father in Heaven,

1070
00:55:33,760 --> 00:55:37,670
而且他应允将永生…
who has promised us eternal life.

1071
00:55:39,320 --> 00:55:41,270
我们是张麻子张大爷的队伍！
We're from "Pocky" Zhang's gang.

1072
00:55:41,880 --> 00:55:43,270
要钱！不要命！
We're here for the money.

1073
00:55:43,680 --> 00:55:44,630
各位乡绅受惊了
Sorry for the intrusion!

1074
00:55:44,800 --> 00:55:46,110
我们今天就是来找几个人
We're looking for...

1075
00:55:46,280 --> 00:55:49,870
黄四郎！城南两大家族！站出来
Huang, heads of families, show yourselves!

1076
00:55:57,400 --> 00:55:58,270
胡万？
Hu Wan?

1077
00:55:59,920 --> 00:56:01,590
神父 打扰了
Father, our apologies.

1078
00:56:02,040 --> 00:56:02,590
各位父老
Ladies and gentlemen,

1079
00:56:02,760 --> 00:56:04,510
剩下的事情就与你们无关了
the rest has nothing to do with this.

1080
00:56:04,680 --> 00:56:05,630
再见
Leave!

1081
00:56:06,040 --> 00:56:06,950
入袋
Gag them!

1082
00:56:08,640 --> 00:56:09,550
起来
Get up!

1083
00:56:11,760 --> 00:56:13,270
好汉！我是本县县长
I'm the governor of this county.

1084
00:56:13,440 --> 00:56:14,420
要绑 绑我吧
I volunteer to be your hostage.

1085
00:56:14,640 --> 00:56:15,620
你不说话不行吗！
Just shut up!

1086
00:56:15,800 --> 00:56:17,430
留着你的命 活着替我们收钱
We spare you to deliver our ransom.

1087
00:56:17,640 --> 00:56:19,350
三天之内 钱到 放人
Three days, pay up and they go home.

1088
00:56:19,600 --> 00:56:20,950
钱不到 撕票打死我吧
- If not, they die. - Shoot me first!

1089
00:56:21,120 --> 00:56:22,430
别打别打！打死我！
- Stop it! - Shoot me first!

1090
00:56:22,640 --> 00:56:23,430
找打是吧
You're asking for it.

1091
00:56:24,160 --> 00:56:26,030
打…！
Beat him up!

1092
00:56:26,200 --> 00:56:27,830
你怎么这么多嘴啊！
You talk too much!

1093
00:56:28,320 --> 00:56:30,230
让你多嘴
I'll teach you a lesson!

1094
00:56:33,720 --> 00:56:35,830
你装模做样的带我的九筒干什么
Stop messing with my mask!

1095
00:56:36,000 --> 00:56:36,750
别把事给我办砸了！
Don't screw things up.

1096
00:56:37,320 --> 00:56:37,990
带走！
Take them away!

1097
00:56:39,200 --> 00:56:40,340
-是他！     -老三！
- It's him. - Three!

1098
00:56:40,560 --> 00:56:41,510
装箱
Pack them!

1099
00:56:43,800 --> 00:56:44,990
不见钱不放人啊！
No one goes until we get his ransom.

1100
00:56:45,800 --> 00:56:47,870
千哥 忍着！
Butler, stay calm!

1101
00:56:50,400 --> 00:56:52,270
One, two, three...

1102
00:56:52,760 --> 00:56:54,110
黄四郎在里头
Huang is in there!

1103
00:56:54,280 --> 00:56:55,950
One, two, three...

1104
00:56:56,840 --> 00:56:58,510
你抱着我夫人学我哭的时候
You plotted this scheme

1105
00:56:58,680 --> 00:56:59,590
就想到这招了
over my wife's dead body?

1106
00:56:59,760 --> 00:57:00,670
有粗有细啊！
I am impressed!

1107
00:57:00,840 --> 00:57:02,710
三天之内 钱不到就撕票！
We'll kill the hostages in 3 days!

1108
00:57:02,880 --> 00:57:05,550
记着 我是九筒！
Remember, I am Nine!

1109
00:57:08,400 --> 00:57:09,950
这活办的真麻利！
That was quite a show.

1110
00:57:10,120 --> 00:57:11,510
-像真的吗？     -像！
- Almost pass for real! - Sure.

1111
00:57:11,680 --> 00:57:14,190
要是有人再流点血就更像真的了！
It'll be more convincing with some blood.

1112
00:57:14,360 --> 00:57:15,340
对！
Right!

1113
00:57:16,840 --> 00:57:18,190
有这个必要吗？
Was that necessary?

1114
00:57:18,360 --> 00:57:20,710
有这个必要吗？有这个必要吗？
Was that really necessary?

1115
00:57:28,240 --> 00:57:29,950
给我打！给我狠狠打！
Shoot! Give them hell!

1116
00:57:30,120 --> 00:57:32,350
千爷 别打了
Butler, hold your fire!

1117
00:57:32,560 --> 00:57:34,350
赶紧回去备银子吧！
We need time to prepare the ransom.

1118
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:38,150
三天收不到钱 麻匪可是要撕票的！
Otherwise they will kill the hostages.

1119
00:57:38,320 --> 00:57:40,350
撕！让他们撕！
Let them kill the hostages.

1120
00:57:40,560 --> 00:57:42,860
一定要让他们撕
In fact, I want them dead!

1121
00:57:43,040 --> 00:57:45,870
替身就是为我干这个的
Why do you think I need a double?

1122
00:57:46,040 --> 00:57:48,310
这个钱 我一分钱都不出！
I'll not pay any ransom.

1123
00:57:48,520 --> 00:57:50,510
不过两大家族的钱
But the families will pay up.

1124
00:57:50,680 --> 00:57:52,310
一定会过你们的手
You'll get your money for sure.

1125
00:57:53,240 --> 00:57:54,350
弟弟
Brother,

1126
00:57:55,040 --> 00:57:56,550
不要为我担心啊！
I'm fine.

1127
00:57:56,720 --> 00:57:59,070
千万不要为我担心！
Don't worry about me.

1128
00:58:00,800 --> 00:58:03,230
老爷 我怀疑胡万投靠了张麻子
Hu Wan must have defected to Zhang.

1129
00:58:03,400 --> 00:58:04,350
一定要找到胡万！
He must be found,

1130
00:58:04,560 --> 00:58:07,270
活要见人 死要见尸
dead or alive!

1131
00:58:07,600 --> 00:58:10,550
替身这么有用啊！得空帮我也找一个
A double is useful. Find me one, too.

1132
00:58:10,720 --> 00:58:13,280
张麻子 你真是没羞没臊
Pocky, have you no shame?

1133
00:58:13,440 --> 00:58:14,710
玩砸了！
The game's up!

1134
00:58:14,880 --> 00:58:15,390
砸了吗？
Really?

1135
00:58:15,600 --> 00:58:16,510
砸了
Yes, game's up.

1136
00:58:16,680 --> 00:58:20,710
我怎么觉得…刚开始啊！
The fun has only just begun.

1137
00:58:20,920 --> 00:58:22,630
阿门！
Amen!

1138
00:58:33,240 --> 00:58:34,030
放人！
Release them.

1139
00:58:34,200 --> 00:58:36,660
给你们留个纪念 不准回头 滚！
Here's a souvenir. Don't look back. Scram!

1140
00:58:42,240 --> 00:58:44,950
夫人 你要是晚走两天
Ma'am, if you're still alive,

1141
00:58:45,120 --> 00:58:47,110
就能亲眼看见了
you'd see this for yourself.

1142
00:58:47,280 --> 00:58:49,990
嫂子要是不走 这钱都到不了这桌上
If she was alive, there'll be nothing here.

1143
00:58:50,160 --> 00:58:53,030
对 我老婆的命换来的这些钱
She traded her life for this.

1144
00:58:53,440 --> 00:58:54,910
那我们家小六子的命不算命啊？
Doesn't Six's life count?

1145
00:58:55,080 --> 00:58:55,830
那不一样！
It's different.

1146
00:58:56,000 --> 00:58:56,830
怎么就不一样啊？
Goddamned it isn't!

1147
00:58:57,000 --> 00:58:57,670
夫人！
My wife.

1148
00:58:57,840 --> 00:58:58,350
谁夫人啊？
Whose wife?

1149
00:58:58,560 --> 00:58:59,190
我夫人！
Mine.

1150
00:58:59,360 --> 00:58:59,870
你夫人怎么了？
What about her?

1151
00:59:00,040 --> 00:59:01,950
夫人是被黄四郎杀死的
She was murdered by Huang.

1152
00:59:02,120 --> 00:59:05,110
你们家六爷自残 自杀！
But Six died at his own hands.

1153
00:59:06,000 --> 00:59:06,790
我一枪崩了你
I'll shoot you dead,

1154
00:59:06,960 --> 00:59:08,910
你敢说我们家小六子 找死啊！
for demeaning our Six!

1155
00:59:09,080 --> 00:59:10,430
老二你把枪放下
Two, put down your gun.

1156
00:59:10,640 --> 00:59:11,620
别拿枪对着我
Stop pointing your gun at me!

1157
00:59:11,800 --> 00:59:13,950
我见过土匪 没见过练块的土匪
I've never seen bandits as dumb as you!

1158
00:59:16,440 --> 00:59:18,870
笑什么啊 别笑 别笑！
Stop laughing! Cut it out.

1159
00:59:19,040 --> 00:59:21,910
我是说你们家六爷 你们家六爷这样
I didn't belittle Six! He had courage!

1160
00:59:22,080 --> 00:59:23,140
那是英雄
He was a hero!

1161
00:59:23,360 --> 00:59:24,670
是 是英雄
Yes, he was heroic.

1162
00:59:24,840 --> 00:59:31,020
我老婆睡着觉 就没醒过来
My wife went to sleep and died in bed.

1163
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:33,990
师爷不哭 嫂子也是英雄
Don't cry! Your wife was heroic, too.

1164
00:59:34,360 --> 00:59:36,190
各位哥哥 咱们为什么来了？
Brothers, why are we here?

1165
00:59:36,360 --> 00:59:37,190
钱啊
To get rich!

1166
00:59:37,360 --> 00:59:37,990
钱到了吗？
Have we succeeded?

1167
00:59:38,160 --> 00:59:39,220
到了
Yes, we have.

1168
00:59:40,000 --> 00:59:40,830
走啊！
So let's leave!

1169
00:59:41,000 --> 00:59:41,590
走啊
Let's go.

1170
00:59:41,760 --> 00:59:42,510
那你还哭什么呀？
Why are you still in tears?

1171
00:59:42,680 --> 00:59:43,350
我可以不哭
I'm overjoyed.

1172
00:59:43,560 --> 00:59:44,910
大哥 什么时候走？
Chief, when do we leave?

1173
00:59:47,640 --> 00:59:48,670
不走！
We're not.

1174
00:59:49,040 --> 00:59:51,030
钱不是黄四郎送来的
This is not Huang's money.

1175
00:59:51,200 --> 00:59:54,110
大哥 两大家族的钱不算钱啊？
But the money's still good!

1176
00:59:54,280 --> 00:59:56,630
我要的是黄四郎的钱！
I want Huang's fortune.

1177
00:59:58,000 --> 01:00:00,830
你不刮穷人的钱 也不要大户的钱…
You refuse to take money from rich or poor...

1178
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:04,700
六子 夫人 两条命
The blood debt of Six and Madam,

1179
01:00:04,880 --> 01:00:07,030
必须黄四郎来偿！
must be repaid by Huang!

1180
01:00:07,200 --> 01:00:09,550
你这是玩命啊！赌徒！
You're gambling with our lives!

1181
01:00:09,720 --> 01:00:10,830
这就算赌了？
You call this a gamble?

1182
01:00:11,000 --> 01:00:14,030
算！就是！还赌不赢
Yes, and you'll end up a loser!

1183
01:00:17,560 --> 01:00:18,700
人不走
We're not leaving.

1184
01:00:19,160 --> 01:00:20,270
钱也都不要了！
We don't want this money either.

1185
01:00:20,440 --> 01:00:21,390
发出去！
Give them away.

1186
01:00:21,600 --> 01:00:22,820
可是 大哥
But Chief...

1187
01:00:24,200 --> 01:00:25,870
这钱你都发给谁呢？
Who do you want to give this to?

1188
01:00:26,960 --> 01:00:28,350
发给穷人呗！
To the poor.

1189
01:00:28,720 --> 01:00:30,270
那谁是穷人啊？
Who are the poor?

1190
01:00:30,440 --> 01:00:33,350
谁穷 谁就是穷人
Those in dire need.

1191
01:00:56,960 --> 01:00:58,590
劫我的时候 你戴的就是九筒
You wore "Nine" when you ambushed me.

1192
01:00:58,760 --> 01:00:59,790
我这是多少？
What am I wearing now?

1193
01:00:59,960 --> 01:01:01,180
你自己摸摸
Feel it for yourself.

1194
01:01:02,600 --> 01:01:03,790
一筒
"One"!

1195
01:01:04,840 --> 01:01:05,350
过瘾吗？
Fun, isn't it?

1196
01:01:05,560 --> 01:01:06,430
过瘾！
Brilliant!

1197
01:01:06,640 --> 01:01:08,070
你不就是想当老天爷吗？
Haven't you always wanted to play God?

1198
01:01:08,240 --> 01:01:08,910
是啊
Yes.

1199
01:01:09,080 --> 01:01:11,430
这跟收拾黄四郎有什么关系呀？
What has it got to do with Huang?

1200
01:01:11,600 --> 01:01:14,750
老天爷都能当 还收拾不了一个黄四郎？
If I am God, ridding him should be a piece of cake.

1201
01:01:26,520 --> 01:01:27,950
这个 我认识
I think I know her.

1202
01:01:28,120 --> 01:01:29,260
我也认识
So do I!

1203
01:01:29,520 --> 01:01:30,910
给她发点钱吧
Let's give her some money.

1204
01:01:31,640 --> 01:01:33,110
干什么呀？
Hang on!

1205
01:01:33,280 --> 01:01:35,950
大哥说了 发穷人！她不穷
She is not exactly poor, is she?

1206
01:01:36,120 --> 01:01:38,310
那你说 谁算穷人？
So who are the poor?

1207
01:01:38,520 --> 01:01:41,990
穷人？那就得被逼得卖儿卖女！
Those who're forced to sell their own children.

1208
01:01:42,160 --> 01:01:45,270
她 就是被穷人卖掉的女儿！
Correct! She was sold by her parents.

1209
01:01:45,520 --> 01:01:46,790
对呀！
Make sense!

1210
01:02:00,280 --> 01:02:02,840
原来县长的人是麻匪！
So you're bandits in disguise!

1211
01:02:03,000 --> 01:02:05,630
我们就想给你发点钱！
We've come to give you money.

1212
01:02:06,640 --> 01:02:08,390
杀！必须的！
Kill her. No option!

1213
01:02:13,560 --> 01:02:16,830
见过麻匪真面目的 必死无疑！
Whoever sees a bandit's face has to die.

1214
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:18,510
这可是你下的令
It's your own rule.

1215
01:02:18,680 --> 01:02:19,870
师爷
Counselor.

1216
01:02:20,600 --> 01:02:22,750
第一个见过麻匪真面目的人
The first to see our faces

1217
01:02:22,920 --> 01:02:24,230
是你！
was you!

1218
01:02:24,800 --> 01:02:27,260
事还没办呢就起内讧！
Our mission is only half accomplished,

1219
01:02:27,440 --> 01:02:29,510
还为了一个女人
and we're bickering over a broad!

1220
01:02:43,360 --> 01:02:46,950
我进城那天 带头敲鼓的是你吧
You're the lead drummer at my inauguration?

1221
01:02:48,400 --> 01:02:50,860
姑娘 贵姓？
What's your name?

1222
01:02:51,080 --> 01:02:53,230
不客气 花姐
Call me Flora.

1223
01:02:53,600 --> 01:02:55,590
不是姓黄吧？
Are you related to Huang?

1224
01:02:55,880 --> 01:02:58,590
不姓！是黄四郎把我买来的
No, he bought me.

1225
01:03:00,320 --> 01:03:03,030
城门口贴的那些告示
There are posters by the city gate.

1226
01:03:03,360 --> 01:03:04,990
知道是什么意思吧？
Know what they're for?

1227
01:03:05,600 --> 01:03:07,270
通缉张麻子的
Bounty offers for "Pocky" Zhang.

1228
01:03:09,000 --> 01:03:11,380
我就是张麻子
I am "Pocky" Zhang.

1229
01:03:12,960 --> 01:03:15,790
麻匪发的 铁证如山！
The bandits were behind this.

1230
01:03:16,360 --> 01:03:20,550
用面具的就是麻匪？我们也有面具
Is it because of the masks? We have masks too!

1231
01:03:20,800 --> 01:03:22,270
那就是县长？
Then it must be the Governor!

1232
01:03:24,240 --> 01:03:26,950
有钱不赚 发给穷人
He is giving money to the poor?

1233
01:03:30,040 --> 01:03:32,600
这像是个买官的县长做的事吗？
No bogus governor would do that.

1234
01:03:35,120 --> 01:03:38,030
今天 我要你们扮成麻匪
I want you to dress up as bandits.

1235
01:03:38,200 --> 01:03:39,830
跟他们一模一样
Exactly like them.

1236
01:03:40,000 --> 01:03:42,830
他们怎么发 你们就怎么抢！
What they give out, you take away.

1237
01:03:43,120 --> 01:03:44,180
搞乱他们！
Let's cause havoc!

1238
01:03:44,640 --> 01:03:45,510
明白！
Understood.

1239
01:03:45,680 --> 01:03:48,790
三步棋必治他于死地
I'll have him checkmate in 3 moves!

1240
01:03:49,600 --> 01:03:52,430
老爷 三步棋 咱们都已经走完了
But we've made 3 moves already.

1241
01:03:53,160 --> 01:03:53,630
是吗？
Really?

1242
01:03:53,760 --> 01:03:55,670
逼死小六子 杀鸡取卵…
Driving Six to death,
killing the chicken for the eggs...

1243
01:03:55,840 --> 01:03:57,230
那是老三步了
Those were old moves!

1244
01:03:57,400 --> 01:03:59,430
现在我要走的新三步
I'm talking about 3 new moves!

1245
01:03:59,640 --> 01:04:02,550
第一步 到省城查清马邦德
First, check out the Governor.

1246
01:04:02,720 --> 01:04:05,870
我总觉得他不像是个买官的县长
He doesn't act like someone who'd buy a post.

1247
01:04:06,600 --> 01:04:08,870
起码 不姓马！
At least, he's not Ma Bangde.

1248
01:04:10,240 --> 01:04:11,550
胡万的事怎么样了？
Have you found Hu Wan?

1249
01:04:12,240 --> 01:04:14,430
胡万？还没找到
Hu Wan? Not yet.

1250
01:04:15,280 --> 01:04:17,310
你怎么可能说还没有找到
How come he is still missing?

1251
01:04:17,520 --> 01:04:19,630
老爷你放心 我会去找他 继续找
Don't worry, sir. I'll find him.

1252
01:04:19,800 --> 01:04:21,070
你晓不晓得…
Do you know...

1253
01:04:22,520 --> 01:04:24,510
我多么的想他
how much I miss him?

1254
01:04:38,160 --> 01:04:40,750
黄老爷盼咐我们把他们搞乱
On master's order, let's wreak havoc!

1255
01:04:41,160 --> 01:04:43,430
看老子怎么把他们搞乱
Let's show how we can mess things up!

1256
01:04:45,880 --> 01:04:46,630
收到银子了？
Did you get your share?

1257
01:04:46,800 --> 01:04:48,270
收到了
Yes.

1258
01:04:49,000 --> 01:04:50,870
那你打算怎么感谢我们
How are you going to thank us?

1259
01:04:51,720 --> 01:04:54,750
怎么感谢都…都行
Any way you like.

1260
01:04:55,320 --> 01:04:58,630
怎么感谢都行？你说的！好！
Any way I like? Great, you said it!

1261
01:05:00,320 --> 01:05:03,750
知道我们…为什么会给你发银子吗？
Know why we gave you money?

1262
01:05:04,080 --> 01:05:06,640
因为麻匪爷对我们好
It is because you're benevolent.

1263
01:05:06,800 --> 01:05:07,940
对你好？
Benevolent?

1264
01:05:08,120 --> 01:05:09,750
还没好透！
We can do even better!

1265
01:05:16,960 --> 01:05:20,580
透！透！透！
Batter! Batter!

1266
01:05:28,120 --> 01:05:31,990
青天大老爷做主啊！
Governor, we want justice!

1267
01:05:32,200 --> 01:05:34,190
砸了你们！砸了！
It's all over! We're finished!

1268
01:05:34,840 --> 01:05:37,270
兔子都知道不吃窝边草
Even rabbits wouldn't do this.

1269
01:05:37,640 --> 01:05:39,940
六个人 还当着人家丈夫
Six men, in front of her husband,

1270
01:05:40,120 --> 01:05:41,230
还让人看
and in broad daylight!

1271
01:05:41,400 --> 01:05:43,350
呸！恶心
Disgusting!

1272
01:05:43,560 --> 01:05:45,030
我都关着灯！
I've never even done this with lights on!

1273
01:05:46,160 --> 01:05:48,350
这种事你们可以花点钱嘛！
If you're desperate, paid for it!

1274
01:05:48,760 --> 01:05:49,950
花点！
Be extravagant!

1275
01:05:50,320 --> 01:05:51,910
哪怕嫖呢！
Visit a brothel!

1276
01:05:52,120 --> 01:05:53,750
花不了多少钱！
It won't cost much!

1277
01:05:53,920 --> 01:05:55,390
哪怕偷偷摸摸的
You don't even have to be discreet.

1278
01:05:56,000 --> 01:05:58,030
简直就是土匪
This is stupid!

1279
01:05:58,200 --> 01:05:59,910
土匪都不如！
You're worse than bandits!

1280
01:06:00,960 --> 01:06:03,110
还说让人家百姓夸你们好
And we'd wanted to leave a good impression!

1281
01:06:03,280 --> 01:06:05,350
就是一句话！恶心！
One word comes to mind: revolting!

1282
01:06:05,560 --> 01:06:07,310
钱肯定是挣不着了！
Our scheme is now in ruin!

1283
01:06:07,560 --> 01:06:09,510
恶心！恶心！
Disgusting!

1284
01:06:09,880 --> 01:06:11,990
恶心呐！恶心！
Filthy, nauseating...

1285
01:06:12,360 --> 01:06:14,790
呸！太恶心！
Revolting!

1286
01:06:24,840 --> 01:06:26,550
大哥 你是了解我的
You know me.

1287
01:06:26,920 --> 01:06:29,150
我从来不做仗势欺人的事
When it comes to this sort of thing,

1288
01:06:29,880 --> 01:06:31,390
我喜欢被动
I prefer to be passive...

1289
01:06:32,600 --> 01:06:34,110
大哥你是了解我的
You know me,

1290
01:06:34,600 --> 01:06:35,870
以我的习惯
I am a lone wolf,

1291
01:06:36,880 --> 01:06:38,430
万事不求人
always acting on my own.

1292
01:06:39,920 --> 01:06:41,950
大哥 你是了解我的
You know me,

1293
01:06:42,280 --> 01:06:43,390
如果是我…
If it was me,

1294
01:06:44,160 --> 01:06:46,030
不会有人活着来告状
she wouldn't have lived to squeal.

1295
01:06:47,560 --> 01:06:48,700
大哥你是了解我的
You know me.

1296
01:06:48,880 --> 01:06:50,550
我老五虽然岁数最大
I may be the eldest,

1297
01:06:50,960 --> 01:06:52,870
我…我至今…
but I am...

1298
01:06:54,840 --> 01:06:56,110
俗称处男
still a virgin.

1299
01:07:00,560 --> 01:07:01,780
别看着我呀
Stop staring at me!

1300
01:07:01,960 --> 01:07:03,950
大哥 你是了解我的
You know me well.

1301
01:07:04,280 --> 01:07:05,630
如果我出手…
If I was responsible,

1302
01:07:05,920 --> 01:07:07,350
那趴在桌子上的
the one on the receiving end,

1303
01:07:08,040 --> 01:07:09,630
应该是她老公
would have been her husband!

1304
01:07:15,200 --> 01:07:19,630
我听出来了 你们都个个身怀绝技
Each of you is so unique.

1305
01:07:21,800 --> 01:07:22,940
但是…
But...

1306
01:07:23,280 --> 01:07:24,070
有人骗了我
I've been betrayed.

1307
01:07:24,240 --> 01:07:25,380
谁呀？谁呀？
By who?

1308
01:07:26,720 --> 01:07:27,940
老汤
Tang!

1309
01:07:28,120 --> 01:07:31,110
这么明显的事 一个师爷看不出来？
How could he overlook the obvious?

1310
01:07:31,440 --> 01:07:34,510
这明明是黄四郎狗狼养的找人冒充的
Huang is behind this scam.

1311
01:07:35,120 --> 01:07:36,990
他今天很反常
Tang's not behaving properly.

1312
01:07:37,240 --> 01:07:38,950
心里一定有鬼
He must be up to something.

1313
01:07:39,880 --> 01:07:42,230
出来！起来！站起来！
Come out! Stand up!

1314
01:07:48,280 --> 01:07:51,790
你最近跟什么人吃过饭？
Who have you been seeing lately?

1315
01:07:52,040 --> 01:07:53,020
见过黄四郎？
Master Huang?

1316
01:07:53,320 --> 01:07:54,190
不许动！举起腿来！
Don't move! Raise your legs.

1317
01:07:54,360 --> 01:07:55,870
谁？！孩子！孩子
- Who's there? - A boy, my child!

1318
01:07:56,000 --> 01:07:57,110
孩子？我的！
- Your child? - Yes, mine.

1319
01:07:57,920 --> 01:07:59,140
你是个孩子？
You're a child?

1320
01:07:59,520 --> 01:08:00,630
几岁？八岁！
- How old are you? - Eight!

1321
01:08:01,080 --> 01:08:02,140
出来！
Come out!

1322
01:08:05,160 --> 01:08:06,300
这是八岁？!
He's eight?

1323
01:08:06,600 --> 01:08:08,150
没人信！我都不信！
I find it hard to believe myself!

1324
01:08:08,320 --> 01:08:09,710
三岁跟他妈一样高
As tall as Mom when he was three.

1325
01:08:09,880 --> 01:08:12,510
五岁就跟我一样高 八岁就这样了
Taller than me when he was five...

1326
01:08:12,800 --> 01:08:14,190
你妈！你妈！
Screw you!

1327
01:08:16,360 --> 01:08:17,070
妈！妈！
Mom, mom!

1328
01:08:17,240 --> 01:08:18,350
你妈！
Screw you!

1329
01:08:18,800 --> 01:08:19,710
敢打俺娃！
Hands off my boy!

1330
01:08:19,920 --> 01:08:23,150
-你妈！     -你妈！
- Screw you! - Screw you, too!

1331
01:08:23,320 --> 01:08:24,710
你妈！
Screw you!

1332
01:08:27,280 --> 01:08:27,950
这是你亲妈？
She's your mother?

1333
01:08:28,120 --> 01:08:28,910
是我妈
Yes, she is.

1334
01:08:29,040 --> 01:08:29,750
这是你亲爹？
And he's your dad?

1335
01:08:29,920 --> 01:08:32,270
我家的事关你屁事啊！你妈！
None of your goddamned business.

1336
01:08:32,960 --> 01:08:33,990
你妈！
Stop it!

1337
01:08:34,560 --> 01:08:35,830
嫂子！怎么回事？
Ma'am, what's going on?

1338
01:08:36,000 --> 01:08:38,030
我是来要钱的 不给钱我不走
I come for money. I won't leave until he pays.

1339
01:08:38,200 --> 01:08:39,180
不给钱不走
He owes you?

1340
01:08:39,360 --> 01:08:43,270
这个老骗子 八年前在俺山西开矿
It was eight years ago in Shanxi.

1341
01:08:43,440 --> 01:08:46,310
骗了钱我就不说了 还骗了我的身子
This crook made me pregnant.

1342
01:08:46,520 --> 01:08:47,710
还不讲信誉
He is a man of poor repute.

1343
01:08:48,120 --> 01:08:49,150
他欠一屁股帐
Ran up a mountain of debts,

1344
01:08:49,320 --> 01:08:50,350
拍屁股走了
then vanished without trace.

1345
01:08:50,560 --> 01:08:53,310
人家问俺追帐 把我六岁的娃给绑了
Creditors kidnapped my younger son.

1346
01:08:53,520 --> 01:08:55,790
当人质呢 不给钱就撕票了！
He'll die if I don't clear his debts.

1347
01:08:55,960 --> 01:08:56,590
那不是我的
He's not my child!

1348
01:08:56,760 --> 01:08:57,740
那就是你的
He is!

1349
01:08:57,960 --> 01:08:59,100
不是我的就是你的！
- He isn't. - He is!

1350
01:08:59,280 --> 01:09:01,230
是你的 我算着日子呢！
He is! I counted the days!

1351
01:09:03,360 --> 01:09:04,750
他骗了人家钱
He swindled someone.

1352
01:09:05,080 --> 01:09:06,060
人家到你那去要帐
His victims tracked you down,

1353
01:09:06,240 --> 01:09:07,830
把你的小儿子绑架了
and kidnapped your younger son.

1354
01:09:08,720 --> 01:09:09,430
不给钱就撕票
Threatening death...

1355
01:09:09,640 --> 01:09:11,430
撕票 所以我要钱呢！
Yes, so I need the money.

1356
01:09:11,640 --> 01:09:12,670
给钱！
Pay her.

1357
01:09:13,160 --> 01:09:14,380
钱 石头！
Money! The stones...

1358
01:09:16,040 --> 01:09:17,750
嫂子 初次见面
Just a small gift,

1359
01:09:18,240 --> 01:09:19,550
不成敬意
to mark our acquaintance.

1360
01:09:20,120 --> 01:09:22,580
石头我不要 不给钱我不走
I don't want these. I want real money.

1361
01:09:22,760 --> 01:09:24,150
你个傻…
You stupid idiot...

1362
01:09:24,680 --> 01:09:27,140
这比钱值钱！这是宝石
These diamonds are worth a fortune!

1363
01:09:27,320 --> 01:09:29,230
啊！真的！
No kidding?

1364
01:09:32,080 --> 01:09:33,140
自行车
Bicycle!

1365
01:09:33,320 --> 01:09:34,230
这就能骑？
I can ride that?

1366
01:09:34,400 --> 01:09:36,230
我们在上海骑过！
We rode one once in Shanghai.

1367
01:09:36,800 --> 01:09:37,990
你们俩去过上海？
You have been to Shanghai?

1368
01:09:38,240 --> 01:09:39,110
浦东
Pudong!

1369
01:09:39,360 --> 01:09:42,190
不信 骑上准倒！
I'm sure you'd fall over.

1370
01:09:43,440 --> 01:09:45,510
来！试试！
Come on. Try it.

1371
01:09:48,600 --> 01:09:49,660
上来
Hop on!

1372
01:09:52,800 --> 01:09:54,110
走 走了！
Let's go!

1373
01:10:02,640 --> 01:10:03,950
自行车！
Bicycle!

1374
01:10:06,080 --> 01:10:07,430
自行车！
Bicycle!

1375
01:10:09,520 --> 01:10:12,430
可是 人肉的自行车
made of flesh and bones...

1376
01:10:14,440 --> 01:10:15,950
我来错地方了？
Have I come to the wrong place?

1377
01:10:16,440 --> 01:10:18,270
我来的不是时候？
Or at the wrong time?

1378
01:10:18,680 --> 01:10:19,350
接客
Serve your customers.

1379
01:10:19,560 --> 01:10:20,270
他们俩都是
They're my customers.

1380
01:10:20,440 --> 01:10:22,630
我们可是先来的
We're here first.

1381
01:10:22,800 --> 01:10:23,670
付钱了吗？
Have they paid?

1382
01:10:23,840 --> 01:10:25,830
自行车能算钱吗？
The "bicycle ride" doesn't count.

1383
01:10:27,120 --> 01:10:27,870
送客！
Show them out.

1384
01:10:28,040 --> 01:10:29,830
上次我给过你很多钱
But I've paid my dues.

1385
01:10:31,520 --> 01:10:32,660
什么钱？
With what?

1386
01:10:33,680 --> 01:10:36,190
窗户外边扔进来的银子？
Money you received through the window?

1387
01:10:36,880 --> 01:10:38,830
那不是麻匪扔进来的吗？
Isn't that bandit money?

1388
01:10:40,400 --> 01:10:42,700
难道他们俩是麻匪？
I wonder if they are also bandits.

1389
01:10:42,880 --> 01:10:45,790
他们不是麻匪 他们是官府的人
No, they work for the Governor.

1390
01:10:47,040 --> 01:10:49,500
你敢拿麻匪的钱给他们付帐？
How dare you pay their tab with bandit money?

1391
01:10:49,680 --> 01:10:51,550
别废话！先把人放了 快点！
Cut the crap! Let her go!

1392
01:10:54,040 --> 01:10:55,830
英雄救美！
White knights to the rescue!

1393
01:10:57,560 --> 01:10:59,350
英雄救美！
White knights to the rescue!

1394
01:11:01,920 --> 01:11:05,430
就算他们是英雄 我也不是美人
I'm no damsel in distress.

1395
01:11:06,200 --> 01:11:09,870
就算我是美人 他们也不是英雄
They're no knights in shining armour.

1396
01:11:32,000 --> 01:11:34,030
老爷 毕竟他们是客人
After all, they're customers.

1397
01:11:34,200 --> 01:11:37,230
今天晚上的钱 我替他们付了
I've already settled their bills.

1398
01:11:37,600 --> 01:11:39,110
您不是常教育我们吗
You taught me yourself,

1399
01:11:39,280 --> 01:11:41,070
客人永远是上帝
customers are always supreme!

1400
01:11:41,360 --> 01:11:42,910
您说对口马？
Isn't that right?

1401
01:11:46,800 --> 01:11:47,830
对！
Yes!

1402
01:11:48,520 --> 01:11:49,580
对！
Correct!

1403
01:12:05,760 --> 01:12:08,950
这就不是英雄救美了
Instead of knights coming to your rescue,

1404
01:12:09,520 --> 01:12:11,710
是美救英雄
they are being saved by a damsel.

1405
01:12:13,040 --> 01:12:17,150
你呀 快成小凤仙儿了
You're turning into a Mata Hari.

1406
01:12:29,680 --> 01:12:30,790
你得罪他了！
You've just pissed him off.

1407
01:12:31,040 --> 01:12:32,310
黄四郎不用得罪
He doesn't need to be pissed off.

1408
01:12:32,520 --> 01:12:33,950
他想让谁死
If he wants you dead,

1409
01:12:34,120 --> 01:12:35,550
谁就得死！
you die!

1410
01:12:35,720 --> 01:12:37,550
我刚才干嘛不一枪打死他呢？
I should've put a bullet through his head.

1411
01:12:37,720 --> 01:12:39,430
我一枪打死他不就完了么！
That would be the end of it.

1412
01:12:40,120 --> 01:12:41,070
别傻了！
Don't be silly.

1413
01:12:41,240 --> 01:12:44,270
大哥说了 留着他是要弄他的钱
Chief wants to go after his fortune.

1414
01:12:45,320 --> 01:12:48,270
既然想弄钱 那…
If you're here for the money, then...

1415
01:12:48,600 --> 01:12:50,550
你们干嘛到处发钱啊？
why are you giving it away?

1416
01:12:52,240 --> 01:12:52,790
这颜色行么
Is this the right colour?

1417
01:12:52,960 --> 01:12:54,270
把伞拿了
Lower the umbrella.

1418
01:12:54,840 --> 01:12:57,270
红倒是够了 你…你过来
The red is fine. Come over here!

1419
01:12:58,440 --> 01:13:00,350
先是绿 再弄红
First apply green, then red.

1420
01:13:00,560 --> 01:13:01,430
明白
Okay, got it.

1421
01:13:01,640 --> 01:13:02,910
明白这意思吧？
Understand?

1422
01:13:04,280 --> 01:13:05,500
你把那锁好了啊
Don't forget to lock up.

1423
01:13:05,680 --> 01:13:06,990
-带上铁锹     -知道了
- Bring the shovels. - Got it.

1424
01:13:07,200 --> 01:13:09,390
-六把铁锹     -知道了
- Six shovels! - Got it.

1425
01:13:13,080 --> 01:13:13,750
大哥你看我…
Chief, how do I look?

1426
01:13:13,920 --> 01:13:16,830
头不用梳了 脸够红 你过来！
Hair is fine. Face is flushed. Come here...

1427
01:13:17,200 --> 01:13:19,430
死人的脸是绿的 加上点别的色
Apply that to a dead man's face

1428
01:13:19,640 --> 01:13:20,860
然后再变成这种红
will turn it into pinkish red.

1429
01:13:21,040 --> 01:13:22,590
明白了明白了日巴
- Got it. - Good.

1430
01:13:22,760 --> 01:13:23,670
绿
Green.

1431
01:13:24,800 --> 01:13:25,990
你过来
Come here.

1432
01:13:26,600 --> 01:13:27,790
绿在底下
Green is the base colour.

1433
01:13:28,040 --> 01:13:30,110
加上那个再变成这个就对了！
Add that and you'll get this!

1434
01:13:30,680 --> 01:13:32,870
-明白了     -明白吗
- Oh, I see... - Got it?

1435
01:13:33,040 --> 01:13:33,950
是这样的铁锹吗？
You want shovels like these?

1436
01:13:34,120 --> 01:13:35,180
锯短 装包里
Shorten them and put them in the bag.

1437
01:13:35,360 --> 01:13:35,910
多短？
How short?

1438
01:13:36,080 --> 01:13:37,190
能装包里
Short enough for the bag.

1439
01:13:37,320 --> 01:13:38,830
快去啊 六把啊
Hurry up! Six shovels!

1440
01:13:39,000 --> 01:13:40,110
去哪啊这是？
Where are you going?

1441
01:13:40,280 --> 01:13:41,670
怎么还扮上了？
What's with the make-up?

1442
01:13:41,840 --> 01:13:43,190
不是要跑吧？
Are you leaving for good?

1443
01:13:45,040 --> 01:13:47,550
你去不去？我们去发钱
Come with us to give out money?

1444
01:13:47,720 --> 01:13:48,910
糟践东西 不去！
No, what a waste!

1445
01:13:49,080 --> 01:13:50,030
不去是吧不去
- So you're not coming? - No.

1446
01:13:54,840 --> 01:13:55,630
那我告诉你
Now listen.

1447
01:13:55,800 --> 01:13:57,550
我这次去 可能回得来
This time, I may come back,

1448
01:13:57,720 --> 01:13:58,910
也可能回不来
but, then again, I may not.

1449
01:13:59,080 --> 01:14:01,030
我要是回来 你就跟我跑
If I do, you can leave with us.

1450
01:14:01,240 --> 01:14:03,870
我要是回不来 你就自己跑
If not, you plan your own getaway.

1451
01:14:04,040 --> 01:14:05,910
去…去哪啊？不是发钱吗？
Aren't you just giving out money?

1452
01:14:06,080 --> 01:14:06,990
是发钱
Yes, we are.

1453
01:14:07,160 --> 01:14:08,350
还有…
By the way,

1454
01:14:11,840 --> 01:14:13,110
半夜的时候
at midnight tonight,

1455
01:14:13,760 --> 01:14:15,630
可能有人来找你
someone may come calling.

1456
01:14:15,800 --> 01:14:17,350
他要找你聊什么
Engage him in conversation.

1457
01:14:17,600 --> 01:14:19,150
你就跟他聊什么
Whatever the topics,

1458
01:14:19,600 --> 01:14:22,270
他怎么聊 你就怎么聊
just chat along with him.

1459
01:14:22,720 --> 01:14:24,030
但是…
But...

1460
01:14:24,240 --> 01:14:27,110
要慢 沉住气
you have to stay calm,

1461
01:14:27,320 --> 01:14:29,350
越慢越好
make it nice and slow.

1462
01:14:29,960 --> 01:14:30,990
你亲眼看见的？
You saw it with your own eyes?

1463
01:14:31,160 --> 01:14:32,070
我亲眼看见的！
Indeed.

1464
01:14:32,280 --> 01:14:36,060
你亲眼看见县长亲自带队出发？
You saw the Governor leading his men out?

1465
01:14:36,280 --> 01:14:36,950
我亲眼看见了！
Yes, with my own eyes.

1466
01:14:37,120 --> 01:14:39,310
你亲眼看见县长亲自带队出发去发钱？
They've gone to give out money?

1467
01:14:39,520 --> 01:14:40,550
我亲眼看见了！
Yes, indeed.

1468
01:14:40,720 --> 01:14:41,750
他戴的是几筒？
Which mask does he wear?

1469
01:14:41,920 --> 01:14:42,510
九筒！
"Nine".

1470
01:14:42,680 --> 01:14:46,590
好极了！今晚不抢钱 杀人！
Splendid. Tonight we shall only kill!

1471
01:14:46,760 --> 01:14:47,390
杀谁？
Our target?

1472
01:14:47,600 --> 01:14:48,710
戴九筒的县长！
The Governor, wearing "Nine"!

1473
01:14:48,880 --> 01:14:52,500
杀县长不用戴面具 您等着验尸吧
Masked or not, consider this done!

1474
01:14:52,680 --> 01:14:54,750
回来！全给我戴上！
All of you, put on your masks!

1475
01:14:56,080 --> 01:14:57,430
麻匪火拼
"Firefight with bandits,

1476
01:14:58,160 --> 01:15:00,230
县长暴死
intrepid Governor killed!"

1477
01:15:01,200 --> 01:15:04,900
听着多么顺耳！
That would be music to my ears!

1478
01:15:13,800 --> 01:15:16,430
看清楚了 他们领头的戴几筒？
Which mask is their leader wearing?

1479
01:15:16,640 --> 01:15:17,700
九筒！
"Nine".

1480
01:15:17,960 --> 01:15:19,630
全都换上四筒！
Let's all change to "four"!

1481
01:15:20,960 --> 01:15:23,630
四筒是自己人 其他人全打死
Kill anyone who is not a "four"!

1482
01:15:23,840 --> 01:15:25,790
那边领头的戴的是几筒 看见了吗？
Which mask is their leader wearing?

1483
01:15:25,960 --> 01:15:27,100
四筒
"Four".

1484
01:15:27,320 --> 01:15:28,910
那咱们应该戴几筒 你知道吗？
Know what we'll be wearing, then?

1485
01:15:29,080 --> 01:15:29,990
明白
Got it.

1486
01:15:30,160 --> 01:15:32,190
先弄死九筒！走！
Let's get rid of "Nine"!

1487
01:15:52,840 --> 01:15:55,070
黄老爷 你怎么在这啊？
Master Huang, what brings you here?

1488
01:15:55,840 --> 01:15:57,790
县衙我不能来吗？
Can I not visit the magistracy?

1489
01:15:59,240 --> 01:16:00,550
点上
Light it!

1490
01:16:00,960 --> 01:16:04,950
你们玩空城计 我就趁虚而入！
When the cat prowls, the mouse seizes control!

1491
01:16:07,080 --> 01:16:08,350
坐
Sit down!

1492
01:16:11,880 --> 01:16:13,350
县长呢？
Where's the Governor?

1493
01:16:18,520 --> 01:16:20,550
都是四筒 下不了手啊！
Everyone is a "Four"? I'm confused!

1494
01:16:20,720 --> 01:16:21,670
下不了手
I'm confused, too!

1495
01:16:21,840 --> 01:16:23,950
打雷天站在雨里头有点不讲究
It's bad to stay out in a thunderstorm.

1496
01:16:24,120 --> 01:16:24,990
太不讲究！
Yes, it's awful.

1497
01:16:25,160 --> 01:16:27,030
那改天再约 撤吧
Let's reschedule. Split!

1498
01:16:27,200 --> 01:16:28,150
撤！
Be in touch!

1499
01:16:28,320 --> 01:16:29,230
怎么撤？
What now?

1500
01:16:29,400 --> 01:16:30,710
从哪儿来 回哪儿去呗
It's back to square one.

1501
01:16:30,880 --> 01:16:32,630
好 从哪儿来 回哪儿去
Yes, square one.

1502
01:16:32,960 --> 01:16:35,260
一二三 撤！
Split! 1, 2, 3.

1503
01:16:46,560 --> 01:16:49,630
听 枪一响 就有人死
Listen! Someone's been shot.

1504
01:16:49,880 --> 01:16:52,630
有人死 就有人哭
Soon someone will mourn.

1505
01:16:53,160 --> 01:16:56,940
人一哭 就要说心里话
Mourning will lead to confessions.

1506
01:16:58,880 --> 01:17:00,150
说吧
Confess!

1507
01:17:01,000 --> 01:17:04,030
你至少有三句要说
You've at least three confessions to make.

1508
01:17:04,960 --> 01:17:06,990
我不该拿你的钻石送人
I shouldn't have given your diamonds away.

1509
01:17:14,560 --> 01:17:16,110
不是这句
Try again.

1510
01:17:17,040 --> 01:17:18,910
杀人诛心是我说的
I suggested "to kill someone,
first destroy his soul".

1511
01:17:19,320 --> 01:17:21,430
也不是这句
Not that either.

1512
01:17:26,200 --> 01:17:28,710
鸿门宴要是我们请就好了
We should have hosted the banquet instead.

1513
01:17:29,440 --> 01:17:30,990
鸿门宴？
The banquet?

1514
01:17:35,960 --> 01:17:37,180
听不见
I can't hear you.

1515
01:17:41,000 --> 01:17:42,060
听不见！
I can't hear you!

1516
01:17:42,240 --> 01:17:43,300
城里麻匪火拼
There was a shoot-out.

1517
01:17:43,520 --> 01:17:46,670
死了六个人！咱们的人安然无恙！
Six killed. We're unscathed.

1518
01:17:55,960 --> 01:17:58,230
师爷 来来 请
Counselor, come take a look.

1519
01:18:01,120 --> 01:18:03,550
或许…是你的恩人呐
Your saviour may be among them.

1520
01:18:03,720 --> 01:18:05,830
您才是我的恩人
No, you are my saviour.

1521
01:18:08,400 --> 01:18:09,830
既然我是你的恩人
If that is the case,

1522
01:18:10,000 --> 01:18:11,630
那就听恩人的话 揭开看看
remove his mask,

1523
01:18:11,800 --> 01:18:12,630
去吧 看看！
and have a good look.

1524
01:18:12,800 --> 01:18:14,910
来！照上照上！
Come on, lights!

1525
01:18:21,000 --> 01:18:22,350
什么情况？
What's going on?

1526
01:18:22,560 --> 01:18:24,550
什么情况？什么情况？
What's happening here?

1527
01:18:27,960 --> 01:18:29,020
胡万！
It's Hu Wan!

1528
01:18:29,320 --> 01:18:30,510
胡…胡万？
Hu Wan?

1529
01:18:30,680 --> 01:18:32,110
怎么会是胡万？
How come it's Hu Wan?

1530
01:18:32,720 --> 01:18:34,230
怪了
This is weird!

1531
01:18:35,720 --> 01:18:36,110
四筒啊
All those wearing "four"

1532
01:18:36,280 --> 01:18:37,340
全是黄家的人！
are my men!

1533
01:18:37,560 --> 01:18:39,550
麻匪呢？
Where are the bandits?
Where are they?

1534
01:18:39,720 --> 01:18:42,550
胡万 就是麻匪！
Hu Wan was a bandit!

1535
01:18:42,720 --> 01:18:45,020
麻匪 就是胡万！
He was one of them!

1536
01:18:45,560 --> 01:18:48,910
杀县长夫人 绑架豪绅
Murderers and kidnappers,

1537
01:18:49,080 --> 01:18:51,150
祸害鹅城百姓
those who terrorised Goose Town,

1538
01:18:51,320 --> 01:18:54,830
就是你黄老爷家的胡万！
were led by your own Hu Wan!

1539
01:18:55,200 --> 01:18:57,830
我说你为什么不出钱剿匪？
I wondered why you didn't fund the expedition.

1540
01:18:58,000 --> 01:19:01,310
原来你是贼喊捉贼啊！
You may even be the bandit chief himself!

1541
01:19:02,760 --> 01:19:04,190
你拿枪指着我？
You dare to turn your guns on me?

1542
01:19:05,000 --> 01:19:06,510
你拿枪指着我？!
You dare to turn your guns on me?

1543
01:19:07,920 --> 01:19:09,910
你想跟我火拼？
Do you want a shoot-out?

1544
01:19:14,360 --> 01:19:18,140
你们看到了没有！这是当麻匪的下场！
Take a good look at a bandit's fate!

1545
01:19:18,320 --> 01:19:20,700
就算是我亲爹也得死！
I'd still have him shot

1546
01:19:21,200 --> 01:19:22,510
死有余辜！
if he was my father...

1547
01:19:23,840 --> 01:19:25,030
早晚！
sooner or later!

1548
01:19:29,160 --> 01:19:32,990
麻匪胡万又让黄老爷枪毙了五回
You just shot Hu Wan 5 more times.

1549
01:19:33,160 --> 01:19:34,190
大义灭亲？
You want to show justice?

1550
01:19:34,360 --> 01:19:35,910
杀人灭口？
Or to make sure he's dead?

1551
01:19:36,080 --> 01:19:40,790
杀人灭口 你就是麻匪的头子张麻子
Only "Pocky" Zhang would want to silence him.

1552
01:19:41,800 --> 01:19:44,590
要是大义灭亲 那好办！
If you'd only wanted to show justice,

1553
01:19:44,760 --> 01:19:46,590
你出钱 我剿匪！
why not fund my expedition instead.

1554
01:19:46,800 --> 01:19:47,830
好啊！
Done deal!

1555
01:19:48,600 --> 01:19:53,590
三天之后 一定给县长一个惊喜
You shall receive a nice surprise in 3 days.

1556
01:19:53,760 --> 01:19:56,670
汤师爷 他是胡万的恩人
He was Hu Wan's boss.

1557
01:19:56,960 --> 01:19:59,030
现在又成了你的恩人
Now he's your boss, too.

1558
01:19:59,600 --> 01:20:00,710
你给翻译翻译
Please act as our interpreter.

1559
01:20:01,440 --> 01:20:02,870
什么叫惊喜？
What is a "nice surprise"?

1560
01:20:03,400 --> 01:20:05,750
翻译翻译 什么叫惊喜？
Interpret for me.

1561
01:20:05,920 --> 01:20:06,980
这还用翻译？都说了…
There's nothing to interpret

1562
01:20:07,160 --> 01:20:10,510
我让你翻译给我听 什么叫惊喜
What on earth is a "nice surprise"?

1563
01:20:10,680 --> 01:20:11,870
不用翻译 就是惊喜啊
It is what it is.

1564
01:20:12,040 --> 01:20:13,260
难道你听不懂什么叫惊喜
You just don't get it, do you?

1565
01:20:13,440 --> 01:20:16,150
我就想让你翻译翻译 什么叫惊喜！
Go ahead and interpret. What is it?

1566
01:20:16,320 --> 01:20:16,910
惊喜嘛…
A nice surprise!

1567
01:20:17,080 --> 01:20:18,060
翻译出来给我听
Translate for me!

1568
01:20:18,240 --> 01:20:20,950
什么他妈的叫惊喜！
What is this "nice surprise"?

1569
01:20:21,120 --> 01:20:25,070
什么他妈的叫他妈的惊喜！
What is this goddamned "nice surprise"?

1570
01:20:25,240 --> 01:20:27,150
什么他妈的叫惊喜啊？
What is this "nice surprise"?

1571
01:20:27,320 --> 01:20:28,710
惊喜就是三天之后
It means that in 3 days,

1572
01:20:28,880 --> 01:20:31,790
我出一百八十万 给你们出城剿匪
I'll put up $1.8 million for your campaign,

1573
01:20:31,960 --> 01:20:33,180
接上我的腿！
to fix my crippled leg!

1574
01:20:33,360 --> 01:20:34,550
明白了吗？
Is that clear?

1575
01:20:34,720 --> 01:20:36,150
这就是惊喜呀
That's the "nice surprise"!

1576
01:20:36,320 --> 01:20:38,190
翻译翻译
Interpret.

1577
01:20:41,520 --> 01:20:42,030
翻译翻译！
Interpret.

1578
01:20:42,200 --> 01:20:44,070
惊喜就是三天之后
The nice surprise is that,

1579
01:20:44,240 --> 01:20:47,390
给你一百八十万两银子 出城剿匪
he will give you $1.8 million in 3 days,

1580
01:20:47,600 --> 01:20:48,950
接上他的腿
to fund an expedition to fix his broken leg!

1581
01:20:50,840 --> 01:20:52,430
大哥这个是惊喜啊
What a nice surprise!

1582
01:20:52,800 --> 01:20:54,430
小弟我愿意等你三天
I'm willing to wait 3 days.

1583
01:20:58,000 --> 01:20:58,950
黄老爷
Master Huang.

1584
01:20:59,240 --> 01:21:01,800
汤师爷是我的至爱
I adore my Counselor,

1585
01:21:02,280 --> 01:21:05,110
你可不能夺我所爱啊
I can't let you have him.

1586
01:21:06,120 --> 01:21:08,310
了然 了然
Fair enough.

1587
01:21:16,120 --> 01:21:17,230
六子
Six.

1588
01:21:17,840 --> 01:21:20,950
事已经办了九成了
We're almost there.

1589
01:21:22,040 --> 01:21:23,390
算七成吧
Say, 70% done.

1590
01:21:23,760 --> 01:21:25,590
今天我就派你二哥出城
I've asked Two to take off first.

1591
01:21:25,960 --> 01:21:27,790
到青石岭去接应我们
He'll wait for us at Emerald Creek.

1592
01:21:28,200 --> 01:21:31,590
剩下的事 我会说到做到
I will keep my promise.

1593
01:21:35,560 --> 01:21:36,830
你明白了吧？
Know what you have to do?

1594
01:21:37,320 --> 01:21:38,670
明白
Yes.

1595
01:21:42,160 --> 01:21:43,830
一百八十万两银子到手
When $1.8 million is in hand,

1596
01:21:44,000 --> 01:21:47,230
我觉着小六子的仇算是报了
I'll consider Six avenged.

1597
01:21:48,920 --> 01:21:50,110
我觉着啊！
I feel that...

1598
01:21:51,760 --> 01:21:54,790
不光六子 夫人的仇也算报了
my wife's death is also avenged.

1599
01:21:59,000 --> 01:22:02,150
你不会真跟黄四郎玩命吧 恩人呐
Saviour, you still want to kill Huang?

1600
01:22:02,320 --> 01:22:04,510
我不是你恩人 黄四郎才是你恩人
I'm not your saviour. Huang is.

1601
01:22:06,800 --> 01:22:09,310
你是恩人 他不是！
You're my saviour. Not him.

1602
01:22:09,840 --> 01:22:11,870
你当时真的以为我死了？
Did you think I was lying dead back there?

1603
01:22:12,040 --> 01:22:13,990
没有！绝对没有
No, of course not.

1604
01:22:14,160 --> 01:22:14,670
没有？
Sure?

1605
01:22:14,840 --> 01:22:16,390
从没这么想过！
Never crossed my mind.

1606
01:22:21,520 --> 01:22:22,990
我可真算服了你了
I've to hand this to you.

1607
01:22:23,160 --> 01:22:26,070
狸猫变太子 嘎登变出一胡万来
Abracadabra, and Hu Wan magically appeared!

1608
01:22:26,760 --> 01:22:28,670
可是我有一事不明
But I really didn't get it.

1609
01:22:29,520 --> 01:22:30,550
六具尸体
Those six bodies,

1610
01:22:30,760 --> 01:22:32,350
这么长的距离 那么短的时间
such a distance, so little time,

1611
01:22:32,560 --> 01:22:34,710
还抹着红脸蛋 你们是怎么搬来的？
how did you move them so quickly?

1612
01:22:34,880 --> 01:22:37,030
我跟黄四郎可是一路小跑过来的
Huang and I took the shortcut.

1613
01:22:37,200 --> 01:22:38,230
你们搬着六个人
You've to carry six bodies.

1614
01:22:38,400 --> 01:22:39,870
来不及呀！
How did you manage?

1615
01:22:40,200 --> 01:22:43,390
我为什么要把人埋在衙门里
They weren't buried at the magistracy.

1616
01:22:43,800 --> 01:22:45,310
我把人就埋在了那！
The bodies were buried there all along.

1617
01:22:46,840 --> 01:22:49,590
人埋在哪儿 事儿就出在哪儿！
I ensure the standoff was at their burial site.

1618
01:22:50,080 --> 01:22:53,510
事儿出在哪儿 黄四郎就得跟到哪儿！
That's where I led Huang to.

1619
01:22:55,920 --> 01:22:57,990
那你真是张麻子
I'm convinced you're "Pocky" Zhang.

1620
01:22:59,800 --> 01:23:00,910
坐！
Sit down.

1621
01:23:05,680 --> 01:23:06,990
我姓张
My name is Zhang.

1622
01:23:07,200 --> 01:23:08,030
知道
I know that.

1623
01:23:08,200 --> 01:23:09,390
叫牧之
Zhang Muzhi.

1624
01:23:09,600 --> 01:23:11,110
好名字！
A fine name!

1625
01:23:11,280 --> 01:23:13,510
兖州牧 豫州牧
It has auspicious meanings.

1626
01:23:13,800 --> 01:23:18,070
牧之 令尊是望子成大器
You father must have high hopes.

1627
01:23:18,600 --> 01:23:20,110
从讲武堂出来
After graduating from military academy,

1628
01:23:20,920 --> 01:23:23,910
我追随过松坡将军
I enlisted in General Cai's army.

1629
01:23:24,360 --> 01:23:26,390
给他做过手枪队长
Served as captain of his riflemen.

1630
01:23:26,760 --> 01:23:28,070
那年你多大？
How old were you then?

1631
01:23:28,240 --> 01:23:29,510
十七
Seventeen.

1632
01:23:29,800 --> 01:23:31,710
少年得志啊
A youthful genius!

1633
01:23:32,360 --> 01:23:36,110
后来庐州会战 将军负了伤
Cai was wounded during the Battle of Luzhou,

1634
01:23:36,880 --> 01:23:39,790
再后来 将军死在了日本
and later died in exile in Japan.

1635
01:23:40,000 --> 01:23:41,270
我回来了
I came back alone.

1636
01:23:41,960 --> 01:23:47,230
碰上军阀混战 天下大乱
The country was in total chaos.

1637
01:23:47,920 --> 01:23:51,620
我只得浪迹江湖 落草为寇
So I became a bandit.

1638
01:23:51,840 --> 01:23:55,190
牧之也被叫成了麻子
They nicknamed me "Pocky".

1639
01:23:56,120 --> 01:24:00,430
可惜啊！多好的一个牧字
Shame! You're so handsome.

1640
01:24:00,640 --> 01:24:02,550
人们不愿意相信
People have an odd way of thinking,

1641
01:24:02,920 --> 01:24:06,030
一个土匪的名字叫牧之
that bandits shouldn't have proper names.

1642
01:24:06,360 --> 01:24:08,710
人们更愿意相信他叫麻子
They love calling their bandits "Pocky".

1643
01:24:08,880 --> 01:24:10,790
人们特别愿意相信
Not only that,

1644
01:24:11,560 --> 01:24:15,340
他的脸上应该长着麻子
they want their bandits scarred and scary.

1645
01:24:17,880 --> 01:24:19,670
这人可真够操蛋的
People can be so ignorant.

1646
01:24:20,880 --> 01:24:24,710
我的故事…却是这样…
My own story started like this...

1647
01:24:25,400 --> 01:24:29,710
那年我也十七岁
I too was a tenderly 17,

1648
01:24:30,160 --> 01:24:32,910
她也十七岁
and so was she.

1649
01:24:33,160 --> 01:24:35,870
停！我不愿意听你的故事
Stop, I'm not interested.

1650
01:24:36,000 --> 01:24:39,990
我一般不跟人说心里话
I don't confess to just anyone.

1651
01:24:40,280 --> 01:24:42,230
这都到嘴边了 你不能让我咽回去吧
I've to continue now that I started.

1652
01:24:42,400 --> 01:24:43,620
咽回去吧
Take it back!

1653
01:24:43,800 --> 01:24:45,830
因为你说出来也是假的
It's all made up anyway.

1654
01:24:46,320 --> 01:24:47,750
你是个骗子
You're a conman!

1655
01:24:52,520 --> 01:24:54,590
北国我不知道
In our part of China,

1656
01:24:56,280 --> 01:25:00,990
在我南国 这样的珍藏版地雷
There are only two such landmines.

1657
01:25:01,560 --> 01:25:02,910
只有两颗
Both limited edition.

1658
01:25:13,080 --> 01:25:17,270
Made in USA 一九一零
Made in U.S.A. - 1910!

1659
01:25:18,880 --> 01:25:22,990
砰！一响 它就没了
Bang and everything's in smithereens!

1660
01:25:24,680 --> 01:25:28,670
所以 不带走几条人命
So if it doesn't take some lives with it,

1661
01:25:29,440 --> 01:25:33,350
那就是卑鄙的浪费！
it'd be such a waste.

1662
01:25:33,880 --> 01:25:35,020
那么…
Well...

1663
01:25:35,920 --> 01:25:37,630
另外一颗地雷呢？
where's the other one?

1664
01:25:37,800 --> 01:25:38,510
炸了！
It exploded.

1665
01:25:38,680 --> 01:25:39,230
炸了？
Really?

1666
01:25:39,400 --> 01:25:41,590
辛亥革命的第一响
The first bang during the 1911 Revolution!

1667
01:25:41,760 --> 01:25:43,310
我知道了
Oh yes, I've heard!

1668
01:25:43,520 --> 01:25:45,190
炸在辛亥这个地方了
It went off at Xinhai!

1669
01:25:47,600 --> 01:25:50,750
辛亥不是个地方 是一种革命
Xinhai's not a place! It's a revolutionary icon!

1670
01:25:50,920 --> 01:25:52,710
您要早这么说我就了然了
You should've said so earlier.

1671
01:25:52,880 --> 01:25:54,750
那还是说说这颗吧
Now, tell me about this one.

1672
01:25:54,960 --> 01:25:56,510
谁让你问那颗的？
You must stay focused.

1673
01:25:56,800 --> 01:25:59,310
所以 它要炸得惊天
I want it to shake the world,

1674
01:25:59,520 --> 01:26:02,950
还要动地 还要泣鬼神
I want it to rock and roll!

1675
01:26:03,160 --> 01:26:03,870
了然
Understood.

1676
01:26:04,040 --> 01:26:05,230
选个好地方
Pick a good spot,

1677
01:26:05,960 --> 01:26:07,310
选个好时辰
find an auspicious time...

1678
01:26:07,520 --> 01:26:09,310
那么…炸谁？
So, who's our target?

1679
01:26:09,520 --> 01:26:10,740
你应该问…
You should've asked...

1680
01:26:10,920 --> 01:26:11,670
炸在哪
"Where"?

1681
01:26:11,840 --> 01:26:13,150
炸在哪？
Where, then?

1682
01:26:13,840 --> 01:26:15,270
剿匪的路上
Where the expedition force must pass.

1683
01:26:15,640 --> 01:26:17,940
这么快又要剿匪了？
Yet another expedition?

1684
01:26:18,200 --> 01:26:19,790
那这回我能多分点吧
Can I have a bigger cut this time?

1685
01:26:20,000 --> 01:26:22,950
你要是真的张麻子 钱都给你
You can have it all if you're the real Pocky!

1686
01:26:23,120 --> 01:26:24,750
了然 我是假麻子！
No problem, sir. I'm a fake.

1687
01:26:24,920 --> 01:26:27,070
老爷给我多少那是对我的恩赐
I'll take whatever you can spare.

1688
01:26:27,400 --> 01:26:29,230
那么 什么时候炸？
When do you want it to blow up?

1689
01:26:29,400 --> 01:26:31,630
什么时候炸那是第三步
That's our denouement!

1690
01:26:31,960 --> 01:26:35,110
且让我把第二步慢慢走好
Let's play out our second act slowly.

1691
01:26:35,440 --> 01:26:36,550
都别动！
Hold still!

1692
01:26:37,200 --> 01:26:38,260
让她说！
Let her speak.

1693
01:26:38,920 --> 01:26:40,710
老二不辞而别
Two left without saying goodbye.

1694
01:26:41,640 --> 01:26:43,230
老三又要走了
Now Three is leaving too.

1695
01:26:43,440 --> 01:26:45,270
我们活活的被你们拆散了！
You are tearing us apart!

1696
01:26:46,720 --> 01:26:49,310
女侠 你是为了老二还是为老三啊？
You're doing this for Two or Three?

1697
01:26:49,520 --> 01:26:50,870
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1698
01:26:52,120 --> 01:26:53,430
你左手的意思我懂
I know your left hand's intention,

1699
01:26:53,640 --> 01:26:54,830
右手的意思我也懂
I know your right hand's intention.

1700
01:26:55,000 --> 01:26:56,910
两只手这么待着 我看不懂
But both hands together...I don't get it.

1701
01:26:57,080 --> 01:26:58,790
要么成 要么死
I'd rather be dead!

1702
01:26:58,960 --> 01:26:59,750
AB型！
Typical Scorpian!

1703
01:27:00,320 --> 01:27:01,350
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1704
01:27:02,520 --> 01:27:03,580
你们都坐下
Sit down, all of you.

1705
01:27:04,120 --> 01:27:05,430
我再跟她聊聊
Let me talk to her.

1706
01:27:07,440 --> 01:27:09,740
你是被黄四郎买来的
You were bought by Huang?

1707
01:27:09,920 --> 01:27:10,510
对
Yes.

1708
01:27:10,680 --> 01:27:11,820
-他打过你吗？     -打过
- Been mistreated? - Yes.

1709
01:27:12,040 --> 01:27:13,150
-我打过你么？     -没有
- Have I ever laid hands on you? - No.

1710
01:27:13,320 --> 01:27:14,380
-你恨他吗？     -恨
- Hate him? - Yes.

1711
01:27:14,600 --> 01:27:15,390
-恨我吗？     -不恨
- And me? - No.

1712
01:27:15,600 --> 01:27:17,590
那你不拿枪指着他！你拿枪指着我？
Then why threaten me with a gun?

1713
01:27:17,760 --> 01:27:18,390
因为你是好人
Because you're a good person.

1714
01:27:18,600 --> 01:27:19,790
什么？
What?

1715
01:27:20,240 --> 01:27:22,070
这是什么狗屁道理？
What kind of stupid logic is that?

1716
01:27:22,240 --> 01:27:23,990
好人就得让人拿枪指着？
You threaten me because I'm good?

1717
01:27:25,280 --> 01:27:27,190
花姐 大哥说得对！
Flora, Chief is right!

1718
01:27:27,560 --> 01:27:28,950
回来！坐下！
Go back! Sit down!

1719
01:27:29,560 --> 01:27:30,670
你们这群王八蛋
You bunch of idiots!

1720
01:27:30,880 --> 01:27:32,950
我让你们把钱发给穷人
I told you to give money to the poor.

1721
01:27:33,120 --> 01:27:34,030
你们发给一个女人？
And you gave it to her?

1722
01:27:34,160 --> 01:27:36,620
我说什么来着？没人听啊！
I warned you but nobody listened.

1723
01:27:36,800 --> 01:27:38,550
闭嘴！天生的老骗子！
Shut up! You're a born cheat!

1724
01:27:38,720 --> 01:27:40,150
时时刻刻想骗我！
Always plotting to swindle me.

1725
01:27:40,320 --> 01:27:42,150
跟黄四郎勾勾搭搭！
Working with Huang behind my back.

1726
01:27:42,320 --> 01:27:44,390
一个土匪碰见一个恶霸
When a bandit confronts a godfather,

1727
01:27:44,600 --> 01:27:45,790
多么简单的事！
the outcome should be simple.

1728
01:27:45,960 --> 01:27:47,910
让你们给弄成这么烂七八糟的
How can you screw up so badly?

1729
01:27:48,080 --> 01:27:49,750
你还敢拿枪指着我？
How dare you still point your gun at me?

1730
01:27:50,040 --> 01:27:51,510
不敢拿枪 当不了麻匪
If I don't dare to draw a gun on you,

1731
01:27:51,680 --> 01:27:53,350
我敢拿枪指着你
I'll never make a good bandit.

1732
01:27:54,120 --> 01:27:55,180
我胆儿大吧
I dare you all!

1733
01:27:59,000 --> 01:28:00,790
你们谁给她出的这个主意？
Whose quirky idea is this?

1734
01:28:01,240 --> 01:28:02,350
谁？
Whose?

1735
01:28:03,280 --> 01:28:04,910
我就是跟她说着玩的
I was just teasing her.

1736
01:28:10,520 --> 01:28:11,950
你是想当麻匪？
You want to become one of us?

1737
01:28:12,120 --> 01:28:14,990
对呀！我想跟你们一块儿发钱
Yes, to give money out to the poor,

1738
01:28:15,160 --> 01:28:18,070
把钱袋子扔到窗户里 听他们笑
to hear and share their joy.

1739
01:28:20,560 --> 01:28:21,390
你现在就是了
You're now one of us.

1740
01:28:21,600 --> 01:28:22,740
我还没准备好呢
But I am not prepared.

1741
01:28:22,960 --> 01:28:23,990
不用准备
No need!

1742
01:28:24,160 --> 01:28:25,350
你们都准备过吗？
Did you make preparation?

1743
01:28:25,560 --> 01:28:26,390
没有
No.

1744
01:28:26,600 --> 01:28:27,190
你准备过吗？
How about you?

1745
01:28:27,360 --> 01:28:29,510
没有啊 我吃着火锅唱着歌
I was eating hotpot and singing songs.

1746
01:28:29,680 --> 01:28:32,350
扑通一下掉水里 出来就到这儿了
My train plunged and I ended up here.

1747
01:28:35,920 --> 01:28:37,590
我们要离开鹅城
We're leaving Goose Town soon.

1748
01:28:37,960 --> 01:28:38,750
你就留在鹅城
But you have to stay.

1749
01:28:38,920 --> 01:28:39,830
不！
No.

1750
01:28:40,680 --> 01:28:42,350
当麻匪要听命令
A bandit must have discipline.

1751
01:28:42,560 --> 01:28:43,950
大哥说得对
Chief is right.

1752
01:28:45,400 --> 01:28:46,870
刚才说的也对
But she has a point, too.

1753
01:28:53,040 --> 01:28:55,310
我有个很重要的事交给你
I have an important mission for you.

1754
01:28:56,040 --> 01:28:57,830
我看你挺合适
I think you can manage.

1755
01:28:58,840 --> 01:29:00,350
这就是惊喜！
This is our nice surprise!

1756
01:29:01,320 --> 01:29:02,910
果然是个惊喜
A nice surprise indeed.

1757
01:29:03,800 --> 01:29:05,150
果然他不姓马！
He is not Ma!

1758
01:29:09,280 --> 01:29:10,750
有了这个惊喜
Now that we know,

1759
01:29:13,000 --> 01:29:17,230
我的第二步就能走的更加悠然
My next move can be more leisurely.

1760
01:29:17,400 --> 01:29:18,790
悠然？
Leisurely?

1761
01:29:19,840 --> 01:29:22,270
盗官欺爵 放在前清
Impersonating a governor
warrants capital punishment.

1762
01:29:22,440 --> 01:29:24,150
满门抄斩
His whole clan dies with him!

1763
01:29:24,320 --> 01:29:25,870
老爷 你等着
Master, just you wait.

1764
01:29:26,520 --> 01:29:27,740
我这就一枪崩了他！
I'll go and blow him away!

1765
01:29:27,920 --> 01:29:28,980
不！
No!

1766
01:29:29,160 --> 01:29:30,190
他们死以前
Before they die,

1767
01:29:30,360 --> 01:29:32,950
我还要好好地耍耍这两只猴！
I want to toy with these circus monkeys.

1768
01:29:33,160 --> 01:29:34,270
我的老爷
But Master,

1769
01:29:34,680 --> 01:29:36,590
这两只猴子不值得您耍！
they're not worth your while.

1770
01:29:36,760 --> 01:29:39,270
要耍！一定要耍！
No, I must toy with them!

1771
01:29:39,720 --> 01:29:42,950
不耍猴 我怎么赚到两大家族的钱？
Otherwise, I couldn't get others to pay,

1772
01:29:43,120 --> 01:29:47,150
不耍猴 他们怎么心甘情愿地去剿匪？
the Governor couldn't go and fight the bandits,

1773
01:29:47,400 --> 01:29:51,710
不剿匪 他们怎么能踩到地雷呢？
and they wouldn't trot on my landmine!

1774
01:29:52,080 --> 01:29:53,300
黄四郎有个替身
Huang has a double.

1775
01:29:53,520 --> 01:29:54,830
跟他长得一模一样
They are indistinguishable.

1776
01:29:55,000 --> 01:29:59,070
我弄不清楚他是黄四郎 还是他替身
I can't tell if this is really Huang.

1777
01:29:59,760 --> 01:30:00,820
你帮我去看看
I need you to check for me.

1778
01:30:05,080 --> 01:30:06,060
假的！
He's a fake.

1779
01:30:06,760 --> 01:30:08,070
他不是黄四郎
He's not Huang.

1780
01:30:08,240 --> 01:30:10,270
我已经跟你们说过我不是他
Told you I'm not Huang!

1781
01:30:10,440 --> 01:30:12,390
我真的不是他
I really am not him.

1782
01:30:12,400 --> 01:30:13,230
肯定不是
I'm certain.

1783
01:30:13,400 --> 01:30:14,870
放了我吧 放了我
Let me go.

1784
01:30:15,040 --> 01:30:17,110
那好 你帮我们看住他
Keep an eye on him until our return.

1785
01:30:17,280 --> 01:30:19,910
等我们回来 就用你手里的枪
If you have to, use your guns.

1786
01:30:20,240 --> 01:30:21,790
我不会用枪
I've never used a gun.

1787
01:30:22,120 --> 01:30:23,590
老三 你教教她
Three, show her how.

1788
01:30:41,800 --> 01:30:43,270
这照片是你吗？
Is that your photo?

1789
01:30:43,600 --> 01:30:44,430
是我！
Yes, it's mine.

1790
01:30:45,040 --> 01:30:45,830
是吗？
Sure?

1791
01:30:46,000 --> 01:30:47,110
是
Yes,

1792
01:30:48,000 --> 01:30:50,270
那时候我还很瘦
I was slimmer then.

1793
01:30:50,760 --> 01:30:52,070
这就不是你
I don't think it's you.

1794
01:30:52,360 --> 01:30:53,550
你说他不是我？
It isn't?

1795
01:30:53,800 --> 01:30:54,590
不是！
No, it isn't.

1796
01:30:54,760 --> 01:30:56,230
我说他也不是我！
I don't think so either.

1797
01:30:56,400 --> 01:30:58,630
这根本就不是我！
No, that ain't me.

1798
01:30:59,840 --> 01:31:01,030
那到底是怎么回事？
What is this all about?

1799
01:31:01,200 --> 01:31:03,150
我还想知道是怎么回事
I was totally baffled myself.

1800
01:31:03,680 --> 01:31:07,270
花钱买了个县官 我总得有个证件吧
When I bought the post, I needed papers.

1801
01:31:07,960 --> 01:31:10,870
我去照相馆照相 取照片的时候
I had my picture taken at a gallery,

1802
01:31:11,200 --> 01:31:12,550
他们给我的就是这张
and that's what they gave me.

1803
01:31:12,720 --> 01:31:14,910
我说这不是我 他们说这就是你
I said the man in the photo wasn't me.

1804
01:31:15,240 --> 01:31:18,750
我说他不是我！他们说这就是你
They insisted that it was.

1805
01:31:19,120 --> 01:31:20,830
没办法 我就把它贴在这了
I've no choice but to use it.

1806
01:31:21,320 --> 01:31:22,510
哦！是这样！
Is that so?

1807
01:31:22,800 --> 01:31:24,270
哦什么呀？
Bullshit!

1808
01:31:24,680 --> 01:31:26,510
这明明是我！
That's obviously me!

1809
01:31:27,120 --> 01:31:28,710
我才是马邦德！
I am the real Ma Bangde.

1810
01:31:29,200 --> 01:31:31,190
哦！是这样
Is that so?

1811
01:31:31,320 --> 01:31:34,940
是这样！我进城以前遇见麻匪
I was ambushed by bandits on my way here.

1812
01:31:35,520 --> 01:31:37,670
幸亏有他 才躲过一劫
He saved my life.

1813
01:31:37,840 --> 01:31:40,630
我一想 索性让他假扮县长
So I let him take the post.

1814
01:31:40,800 --> 01:31:43,390
毕竟是自家外甥嘛
After all, he's my nephew.

1815
01:31:43,600 --> 01:31:44,950
三舅 这话能跟他说吗？
Uncle, we shouldn't be telling him this.

1816
01:31:45,120 --> 01:31:46,180
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1817
01:31:46,920 --> 01:31:49,830
黄老爷见笑 马某走南闯北
I've travelled all over China,

1818
01:31:50,000 --> 01:31:52,070
在九个地方做过县长
I have been governor in 9 counties.

1819
01:31:52,240 --> 01:31:56,270
靠的就是以假乱真、鱼目混珠之章法
I excel in confusing facts with fiction!

1820
01:31:56,520 --> 01:31:58,150
那么…马县长…
So, Governor Ma...

1821
01:31:58,320 --> 01:31:59,230
你说
Yes?

1822
01:31:59,960 --> 01:32:01,310
叫我呐！
He's addressing me.

1823
01:32:02,040 --> 01:32:03,020
黄老爷继续
You were saying?

1824
01:32:03,200 --> 01:32:05,190
我刚摸清你们的底细
Just as I uncover the truth,

1825
01:32:05,840 --> 01:32:07,710
你们就不打自招
you blow your own cover!

1826
01:32:08,040 --> 01:32:08,630
太巧了吧？
What a coincidence.

1827
01:32:08,800 --> 01:32:13,110
有道是 展颜消宿怨
"Stop frowning to dispel ill feelings,

1828
01:32:13,280 --> 01:32:15,150
一笑泯恩仇啊
and brush aside quarrels with a smile."

1829
01:32:15,320 --> 01:32:16,790
你想跟我和解？
Want to make peace?

1830
01:32:17,400 --> 01:32:19,110
好啊！我的替身呢？
Splendid. Where's my double?

1831
01:32:19,840 --> 01:32:22,270
还给我 前面的账一笔勾销
Return him and we'll call it quits.

1832
01:32:22,440 --> 01:32:23,630
撕票了
We've killed him.

1833
01:32:24,400 --> 01:32:26,430
哪个王八蛋让你撕票的？
Which asshole ordered his execution?

1834
01:32:26,640 --> 01:32:28,390
你个王八蛋让我撕票的！
You're that asshole!

1835
01:32:31,080 --> 01:32:32,910
开枪 你开枪我也能先打死你
I dare you to pull your trigger!

1836
01:32:33,800 --> 01:32:34,550
放下！
Lay down your guns!

1837
01:32:34,960 --> 01:32:37,150
开枪！你先开枪 我也能先打死你
I know I could take you out first.

1838
01:32:38,400 --> 01:32:41,190
把枪放下！我数三下
Put down your guns on my count of three!

1839
01:32:41,360 --> 01:32:44,070
一！二！三！
One, two, three!

1840
01:32:45,960 --> 01:32:47,270
老黄 你先放下
Huang, put it down!

1841
01:32:47,520 --> 01:32:49,150
他不懂事儿 你也不懂事啊？
He may be a brute, but you too?

1842
01:32:52,800 --> 01:32:54,070
你最不懂事！
You're the worst!

1843
01:32:54,560 --> 01:32:55,750
你们什么时候出城剿匪？
When are you leaving for your expedition?

1844
01:32:55,960 --> 01:32:56,990
走不了
We aren't.

1845
01:32:57,240 --> 01:32:58,550
钱不到手 出不了城
We can't leave without funding.

1846
01:32:58,720 --> 01:33:00,110
出不了城 剿不了匪
We can't fight without leaving!

1847
01:33:00,600 --> 01:33:02,830
黄老爷 您说话不算数啊！
You've failed to live up to your promise.

1848
01:33:03,000 --> 01:33:04,350
鸿门宴上说得好
You had agreed to

1849
01:33:04,560 --> 01:33:05,700
你带头出钱
Iead the contribution

1850
01:33:05,880 --> 01:33:07,750
再套出两大家族的钱来
in order to make the others pay.

1851
01:33:07,920 --> 01:33:09,550
可是你不但不出钱
Not only have you not put up any money,

1852
01:33:09,720 --> 01:33:12,950
还扮成麻匪跟我们打来打去 不仗义啊
you've also fought us posing as bandits!

1853
01:33:13,080 --> 01:33:16,310
错！你们看见的麻匪 是我扮的
Wrong! You saw my men dressed up as bandits.

1854
01:33:17,000 --> 01:33:18,870
我看见的麻匪 是你们扮的
I saw yours posing as bandits, too.

1855
01:33:19,080 --> 01:33:20,510
可是他们看见的麻匪
But when the others see these bandits,

1856
01:33:20,680 --> 01:33:22,430
他们以为是真的！
they wouldn't know that they're fakes.

1857
01:33:22,680 --> 01:33:25,910
现在正是让他们出钱剿匪的好时机！
Now is the time to pay for the expedition.

1858
01:33:26,080 --> 01:33:28,430
只要我出钱 他们一定会出
If I pay, others will follow suit.

1859
01:33:28,640 --> 01:33:30,070
你的钱呢？
Where's your money?

1860
01:33:38,800 --> 01:33:40,830
早已经为你准备好了
It's all here.

1861
01:33:41,320 --> 01:33:43,030
鹅城到处都是我的钱
I've money stowed away everywhere!

1862
01:33:43,360 --> 01:33:44,580
都在这儿？
It's all here?

1863
01:33:44,760 --> 01:33:46,190
这只是一半
This is only half of my share.

1864
01:33:46,440 --> 01:33:50,430
我们想赚多少 他们必须出多少
Each family will have to put up the same.

1865
01:33:50,640 --> 01:33:51,860
三舅 有诈！
Uncle, this is a trap.

1866
01:33:52,800 --> 01:33:53,780
诈？
A trap?

1867
01:33:55,160 --> 01:33:56,910
来回这么多趟 死了这么多人
After all these confrontations,

1868
01:33:57,080 --> 01:33:57,910
他一分钱都不出
he has not put up a dime.

1869
01:33:58,080 --> 01:33:59,990
今天怎么突然出了这么多钱？
Why so generous all of a sudden?

1870
01:34:00,160 --> 01:34:01,190
你觉得突然？
Did I surprise you?

1871
01:34:02,040 --> 01:34:02,630
太突然了
Yes, you did.

1872
01:34:02,800 --> 01:34:04,020
我也觉得突然
I surprised myself too!

1873
01:34:04,320 --> 01:34:05,270
想知道吗？
Want to know why?

1874
01:34:05,760 --> 01:34:06,820
过来
Come here.

1875
01:34:09,000 --> 01:34:10,790
我要当…
I - want - to - be -

1876
01:34:11,160 --> 01:34:11,790
县长
Governor!

1877
01:34:11,960 --> 01:34:13,020
你？
You?

1878
01:34:13,160 --> 01:34:14,670
我做不了县长？
I won't make a Governor?

1879
01:34:15,600 --> 01:34:16,790
我不像个县长？
Don't I look the part?

1880
01:34:16,960 --> 01:34:19,550
像！我们一走 你就上任鹅城
Yes, you can swear in as soon as we leave.

1881
01:34:19,720 --> 01:34:21,150
鹅城？
Goose Town?

1882
01:34:22,320 --> 01:34:24,110
我买了六个县的县长！
I bought governorship of 6 more counties!

1883
01:34:24,280 --> 01:34:26,510
我一个人当不过来
I can't handle all on my own!

1884
01:34:27,040 --> 01:34:28,150
所以…
That is why...

1885
01:34:28,360 --> 01:34:29,420
出去
Get out!

1886
01:34:29,960 --> 01:34:31,310
退下
Leave us.

1887
01:34:32,400 --> 01:34:35,230
老马 你来帮我当三个县的县长
I need you to govern three of them for me.

1888
01:34:35,400 --> 01:34:37,670
好啊！这事我拿手
Brilliant! I'm good at governing.

1889
01:34:37,880 --> 01:34:38,990
等会！
Hey, wait...

1890
01:34:39,160 --> 01:34:41,190
那…那我干什么呀？
What about me, then?

1891
01:34:41,360 --> 01:34:42,550
你嘛…
You...

1892
01:34:43,600 --> 01:34:45,630
来当一个假的张麻子！
can play "Pocky" Zhang!

1893
01:34:47,720 --> 01:34:48,910
好啊
Great idea!

1894
01:35:23,960 --> 01:35:25,830
自宣统皇帝退位以后
Since the abdication of the last Emperor,

1895
01:35:26,840 --> 01:35:29,110
鹅城一共来过51任县长
Goose Town has 51 governors.

1896
01:35:29,240 --> 01:35:33,590
他们都是王八蛋、禽兽、畜生、寄生虫
They're all bastards, parasites and leeches!

1897
01:35:33,760 --> 01:35:36,750
但是这位马邦德县长
But our beloved Governor Ma,

1898
01:35:37,040 --> 01:35:39,070
他不是王八蛋 不是畜生
is neither a bastard, parasite,

1899
01:35:39,240 --> 01:35:41,700
不是禽兽 也不是寄生虫
Ieech, nor a beast!

1900
01:35:41,880 --> 01:35:45,750
他今天亲自带队 出兵剿匪
He risks his life to combat the bandits.

1901
01:35:46,120 --> 01:35:49,390
他是我们的大英雄
He is our hero!

1902
01:35:52,680 --> 01:35:53,900
师爷 请！
Counselor, please.

1903
01:35:56,880 --> 01:36:00,030
大风起兮云飞扬
It's time for heroes to take centre stage!

1904
01:36:00,240 --> 01:36:03,390
安得猛士兮走四方
It's time for heroes to show their mettle!

1905
01:36:03,600 --> 01:36:07,070
麻匪 任何时候都要剿
We must rid ourselves of these bandits.

1906
01:36:07,280 --> 01:36:08,790
不剿不行
We don't have a choice.

1907
01:36:09,000 --> 01:36:11,790
你们想想 你带着老婆
Imagine, if you take your wife out,

1908
01:36:12,440 --> 01:36:15,910
出了城 吃着火锅 还唱着歌
singing, eating hot pot and be merry,

1909
01:36:16,080 --> 01:36:19,270
突然就被麻匪劫了！
when bandits jump on you from nowhere!

1910
01:36:20,040 --> 01:36:22,270
所以 没有麻匪的日子
I long for a world without thieves,

1911
01:36:22,680 --> 01:36:24,550
才是好日子！
for days of wine and roses!

1912
01:36:25,880 --> 01:36:26,990
县长 请！
Governor, please!

1913
01:36:29,160 --> 01:36:31,350
出发！
March!

1914
01:36:46,200 --> 01:36:46,990
恩人
Saviour,

1915
01:36:47,280 --> 01:36:48,670
给你看个宝贝
want to check this out?

1916
01:36:50,160 --> 01:36:51,190
这不就是委任状嘛
Isn't that the warrant?

1917
01:36:51,320 --> 01:36:52,670
念念 念念
Read it out loud.

1918
01:36:54,200 --> 01:36:56,790
兹委任马邦德…怎么了？
Ma Bangde is hereby appointed...

1919
01:36:56,960 --> 01:36:57,830
后面！
Read on!

1920
01:36:58,000 --> 01:36:59,710
中华民国八年八月…
8th month of the 8th year of the Republic...

1921
01:36:59,880 --> 01:37:01,230
念你没念过的字 当中！
Don't miss out the words in between...

1922
01:37:01,400 --> 01:37:04,790
兹委任马邦德为康城县长…
Ma Bangde is hereby appointed
Kang County governor...

1923
01:37:05,560 --> 01:37:06,350
等会…
Hang on...

1924
01:37:07,520 --> 01:37:08,430
康城？
Kang County?

1925
01:37:09,560 --> 01:37:10,510
不是鹅城吗？
Not Goose Town?

1926
01:37:10,680 --> 01:37:12,270
从来都是康城
It has always been Kang County.

1927
01:37:12,440 --> 01:37:12,990
好小子
You bastard!

1928
01:37:13,160 --> 01:37:14,070
怨你啊
Blame yourself!

1929
01:37:14,240 --> 01:37:16,990
你把我泡水里 九筒扣脸上
When you dumped me in the river,

1930
01:37:17,200 --> 01:37:19,580
闹钟咔咔咔响 吓死我了！
scared as I was, I had an inspired moment.

1931
01:37:19,760 --> 01:37:22,320
我灵机一动 让你去鹅城
I brought you to Goose Town.

1932
01:37:22,520 --> 01:37:25,870
这鹅城和康城有什么不一样啊？
What's their difference?

1933
01:37:26,040 --> 01:37:28,710
康城富饶 鹅城凶险
Kang County is affluent. Goose Town is deadly.

1934
01:37:28,880 --> 01:37:30,310
那你为什么让我去啊？
Why Goose Town for me?

1935
01:37:30,520 --> 01:37:32,070
你鬼扯呗 截火车！
You're a tough cookie, aren't you?

1936
01:37:32,240 --> 01:37:36,020
告诉你啊 你进了鹅城就有两种情况
There can only be two outcomes.

1937
01:37:36,240 --> 01:37:39,230
第一 你进城就被黄四郎弄死
Either Huang kills you dead,

1938
01:37:39,400 --> 01:37:41,310
我马走康城 从容上任
and I'll move on to Kang County.

1939
01:37:41,520 --> 01:37:44,350
第二 你有种 咱俩办了黄四郎
Or we sort out Huang instead,

1940
01:37:44,560 --> 01:37:45,780
就像现在这样
Iike what's happening now.

1941
01:37:45,960 --> 01:37:47,910
好！说得好 马邦德
Very clever!

1942
01:37:48,080 --> 01:37:48,870
你这个骗子
You goddamned crook!

1943
01:37:49,040 --> 01:37:50,870
早晚有一天你会被张麻子
One day Pocky will get you,

1944
01:37:51,040 --> 01:37:52,150
一枪崩了
and blast you to hell!

1945
01:37:52,320 --> 01:37:53,150
你崩了我？
You won't.

1946
01:37:53,320 --> 01:37:54,790
你舍不得
You love me too much.

1947
01:37:54,960 --> 01:37:57,710
你还真相信我就是张麻子？
You still think I'm "Pocky" Zhang?

1948
01:37:58,920 --> 01:38:01,030
你要不是张麻子 这山上可就有真麻子
If not, the real one must be somewhere around.

1949
01:38:01,200 --> 01:38:03,070
张麻子一来 你我可就没命了
We're doomed if we run into him!

1950
01:38:03,960 --> 01:38:08,270
张麻子卜二
Speak of the devil!

1951
01:38:14,040 --> 01:38:15,590
告诉弟兄们 散开
Tell our men to hold their fire!

1952
01:38:15,840 --> 01:38:17,710
别开枪 往山顶上跑
Scatter! Run for the peak.

1953
01:38:18,120 --> 01:38:23,910
「大哥有令 散开 别开枪」
"Hold your fire. Scatter!"

1954
01:38:24,080 --> 01:38:30,830
「往山顶上跑 抓住他们的头儿」
"Run for the peak. Grab their leader."

1955
01:38:36,720 --> 01:38:37,630
西边十个
10 to the west.

1956
01:38:38,160 --> 01:38:39,220
南面六个
6 to the south.

1957
01:38:40,080 --> 01:38:41,110
东边还有一大片！
Another group to the east.

1958
01:38:41,320 --> 01:38:42,510
让老七去找老三
Tell Seven to join Three!

1959
01:38:42,960 --> 01:38:44,020
先把西边的收拾掉
Secure our west flank.

1960
01:38:47,640 --> 01:38:52,270
「老七去找老三 干掉西面」
"Seven and Three to secure west flank!"

1961
01:38:57,640 --> 01:38:59,910
「我到了」
"I'm there!"

1962
01:39:00,600 --> 01:39:01,660
「不是十个 是十一个」
"There are 11 of them, not 10!"

1963
01:39:01,840 --> 01:39:04,990
「没事 你四 我七」
"No sweat, let's share them!"

1964
01:39:14,360 --> 01:39:15,230
「落停」
"Done!"

1965
01:39:15,400 --> 01:39:16,870
老三来信 西边搞定
Message from Three. West is secured.

1966
01:39:18,440 --> 01:39:20,900
这鸡叫成电台了 我看行！
These pheasant calls really work wonder!

1967
01:39:21,080 --> 01:39:21,710
告诉他们
Tell them!

1968
01:39:21,880 --> 01:39:23,990
让老三去找老四 把南边干掉
Three joins Four to secure our south.

1969
01:39:24,120 --> 01:39:25,510
老七回来保护师爷！
Seven back to protect the Counselor.

1970
01:39:27,840 --> 01:39:30,790
「老三去找老四 干掉南面」
"Three and Four to secure the south."

1971
01:39:30,960 --> 01:39:34,390
「老七回来保护师爷」
"Seven back to guard the Counselor."

1972
01:39:45,880 --> 01:39:48,180
「我被包围了」
"I'm out-flanked."

1973
01:39:51,720 --> 01:39:52,670
「听我口令 甩斗笠」
"Throw the hats on my signal!"

1974
01:39:52,840 --> 01:39:54,910
「东边归我 西边归你」
"I'll take the east. You the west."

1975
01:40:11,720 --> 01:40:13,590
大哥 老三老四他们得手了
Three and Four are done.

1976
01:40:14,200 --> 01:40:15,910
大哥我到了！大哥我到了！
I'm back. I'm back.

1977
01:40:17,520 --> 01:40:18,310
师爷交给你了 快！
Stay with the Counselor!

1978
01:40:18,520 --> 01:40:19,390
明白！
Understood.

1979
01:40:19,720 --> 01:40:20,780
师爷 快！
Counselor, come!

1980
01:40:24,160 --> 01:40:25,070
三哥！
Three!

1981
01:40:26,520 --> 01:40:27,550
好像是二哥
It looks like Two.

1982
01:40:27,840 --> 01:40:30,350
南国张麻子在此
Pocky Zhang is here.

1983
01:40:31,840 --> 01:40:35,670
钱留下 银子也留下…是二哥
- Leave your money... - It's Two.

1984
01:40:37,080 --> 01:40:38,190
死了吧？
Is he dead?

1985
01:40:45,000 --> 01:40:47,190
我弄死你妈的呀！
Goddamned it!

1986
01:40:51,520 --> 01:40:53,950
告诉弟兄们 上东边去
Tell everyone to go east.

1987
01:40:54,880 --> 01:40:56,430
抓着活的 问出他们头在哪
Bring one in for interrogation.

1988
01:40:56,640 --> 01:40:57,750
我亲手宰了他！
I'll kill their leader myself.

1989
01:40:58,960 --> 01:40:59,990
上东边
Let's move.

1990
01:41:05,400 --> 01:41:05,830
头在哪儿？
Where's your leader?

1991
01:41:06,000 --> 01:41:07,550
北面 脸上有麻子的就是
In the north, with a pockmarked face.

1992
01:41:07,760 --> 01:41:08,900
北面！山顶上
Go north! On the hill.

1993
01:41:14,400 --> 01:41:14,870
我没死吧？
Am I dead?

1994
01:41:15,040 --> 01:41:15,910
没有！没死！
No, you're still alive.

1995
01:41:16,080 --> 01:41:18,190
没死！要说什么？我帮你吹
Do you want to signal a message?

1996
01:41:19,600 --> 01:41:20,790
怎么吹？怎么吹？
How do you whistle?

1997
01:41:30,760 --> 01:41:31,510
你带我走吧！
Can you lead the way?

1998
01:41:31,680 --> 01:41:33,550
不…跑不动
No, I can't run any more.

1999
01:41:33,720 --> 01:41:34,230
我带你走
Follow me, then.

2000
01:41:34,400 --> 01:41:35,620
跑不动…！
I can't run.

2001
01:41:35,800 --> 01:41:36,940
不是嘴坏了吗？
You've only blown up your cheeks.

2002
01:41:37,440 --> 01:41:39,110
嘴坏了用脚跑啊！
Your legs are fine.

2003
01:41:40,760 --> 01:41:46,070
「大哥死了 大哥死了」
"Chief is dead! Chief is dead!"

2004
01:41:47,400 --> 01:41:48,310
大哥死了？
The Chief is dead?

2005
01:41:50,800 --> 01:41:52,150
你把大哥给吹死了
You just signalled the Chief's death!

2006
01:41:52,680 --> 01:41:54,190
老五 你去看看
Five, go check it out.

2007
01:41:55,800 --> 01:41:56,860
大哥
Chief!

2008
01:41:57,640 --> 01:41:58,620
大哥
Chief!

2009
01:41:59,360 --> 01:42:00,420
大哥
Chief!

2010
01:42:01,200 --> 01:42:02,150
他们说你死了！
They said you're dead.

2011
01:42:02,280 --> 01:42:05,150
放他妈的屁！我这不还活着吗？
Bullshit! Am I not alive?

2012
01:42:05,560 --> 01:42:07,790
「大哥没死」
"Chief is alive and well!"

2013
01:42:08,760 --> 01:42:10,150
放他妈的屁怎么没吹啊？
Why missed out signalling "bullshit"?

2014
01:42:10,280 --> 01:42:11,950
「放你妈的屁」
"You're full of shit!"

2015
01:42:12,120 --> 01:42:13,150
听见没
Hear that?

2016
01:42:14,280 --> 01:42:15,910
骂咱们放你娘的屁呢！
He said we're full of shit.

2017
01:42:18,080 --> 01:42:19,110
等会儿
Wait.

2018
01:42:22,880 --> 01:42:24,100
假麻子抓到了
They caught the fake!

2019
01:42:25,360 --> 01:42:26,580
你是张麻子？
You're "Pocky" Zhang?

2020
01:42:27,000 --> 01:42:28,220
你脸上怎么没有麻子呢？
Where are your pockmarks?

2021
01:42:28,640 --> 01:42:29,510
这事谁问谁死！
No one asking that question has survived.

2022
01:42:29,680 --> 01:42:30,950
明白了！不问了
Oops! I take it back.

2023
01:42:32,520 --> 01:42:33,830
我这儿有一宝贝
I've got something special.

2024
01:42:34,160 --> 01:42:35,070
送给你了
You can have them,

2025
01:42:35,240 --> 01:42:36,670
能换我一条命吧？
in exchange for my life.

2026
01:42:39,840 --> 01:42:41,190
那…那两个人呢？
What happened to them?

2027
01:42:41,320 --> 01:42:43,150
说实话能换一条命吧
If I tell you, will you spare me?

2028
01:42:43,320 --> 01:42:43,750
快说！
Speak!

2029
01:42:43,920 --> 01:42:46,110
大个的被我给锯了 比矮个的还矮
I sawed the legs off the tall one.

2030
01:42:46,280 --> 01:42:47,110
矮的呢？
And the short one?

2031
01:42:47,280 --> 01:42:48,190
当场就被吓死了
She died of fright at the sight!

2032
01:42:51,720 --> 01:42:52,190
师爷！
Counselor.

2033
01:42:52,320 --> 01:42:53,430
师爷！师爷！
Counselor...

2034
01:42:53,640 --> 01:42:54,550
谁让你冒充我的？
Who's behind this scam?

2035
01:42:54,720 --> 01:42:55,830
黄老爷
Master Huang.

2036
01:42:56,680 --> 01:42:57,740
麻子哪儿来的？
Nice pockmarks!

2037
01:42:57,920 --> 01:42:58,590
他烫的
He burnt them.

2038
01:42:58,760 --> 01:42:59,740
劫了几任县官？
How many governors have you robbed?

2039
01:42:59,920 --> 01:43:01,190
说出来能换条命吗？
Will you spare me?

2040
01:43:01,360 --> 01:43:01,950
快说！
Speak!

2041
01:43:02,120 --> 01:43:04,790
五回！五个县长全被我给干掉了
I've killed five governors,

2042
01:43:04,960 --> 01:43:06,230
钱我跟黄老爷给分了
and shared the loot with Master Huang.

2043
01:43:06,400 --> 01:43:07,430
那是什么？
What's that?

2044
01:43:07,640 --> 01:43:09,510
万民伞！那五个被我干掉的县长留下的
A governor's silver umbrella.

2045
01:43:09,680 --> 01:43:10,870
全都给你！
Take it!

2046
01:43:11,200 --> 01:43:12,990
-山西往哪边走啊？     -我还有四把呢
- Which way to Shanxi? - I have four more.

2047
01:43:13,160 --> 01:43:14,380
我知道
I know the way.

2048
01:43:14,600 --> 01:43:15,710
说出来能换条人命吧？
Will you spare me if I tell you?

2049
01:43:15,880 --> 01:43:16,860
快他妈说！
Goddamned it! Speak!

2050
01:43:17,040 --> 01:43:18,750
往东！往东！
To the east, to the east!

2051
01:43:19,600 --> 01:43:22,630
哎呀！不能往东！千万不能往东！
Come back! You mustn't go that way!

2052
01:43:29,840 --> 01:43:31,870
山西确实是在东边
But Shanxi really is to our east.

2053
01:43:33,240 --> 01:43:34,350
东边…
East...

2054
01:43:44,440 --> 01:43:47,070
你到底是不是张麻子？
Are you really "Pocky" Zhang?

2055
01:43:47,280 --> 01:43:48,110
我是
Yes, I am.

2056
01:43:48,280 --> 01:43:50,910
我可是快要死的人了
I am about to kick the bucket,

2057
01:43:51,640 --> 01:43:53,350
别骗我
don't lie to me.

2058
01:43:53,920 --> 01:43:55,110
放心
Don't worry.

2059
01:43:56,000 --> 01:43:57,430
我就是张麻子
I really am "Pocky" Zhang.

2060
01:43:58,400 --> 01:44:00,700
麻子
Pocky!

2061
01:44:00,880 --> 01:44:02,910
屁股…
My ass...

2062
01:44:03,520 --> 01:44:05,710
屁股疼
it hurts.

2063
01:44:08,160 --> 01:44:09,300
师爷
Counselor.

2064
01:44:09,880 --> 01:44:11,550
屁股在树上呢
Your ass is on that tree.

2065
01:44:12,240 --> 01:44:13,590
不疼了
You can't feel it.

2066
01:44:16,400 --> 01:44:21,630
我树上的屁股的口袋里
On my ass over there,

2067
01:44:21,800 --> 01:44:23,990
有五张委任状
I have another five warrants.

2068
01:44:24,520 --> 01:44:26,270
都给你
Take them.

2069
01:44:26,800 --> 01:44:31,230
听我的 千万别回鹅城
Promise never to return to Goose Town.

2070
01:44:31,720 --> 01:44:36,350
你呀 弄不过黄四郎
You can't beat Huang.

2071
01:44:36,560 --> 01:44:39,750
带上银子 走吧
Take the money and run.

2072
01:44:40,120 --> 01:44:42,500
你放心 我不回鹅城
Don't worry, I won't go back.

2073
01:44:42,800 --> 01:44:48,550
其实 我还有两档子事儿骗过你
I lied about two other things.

2074
01:44:49,240 --> 01:44:50,590
骗了就骗了吧
No big deal.

2075
01:44:50,760 --> 01:44:52,270
不行
No.

2076
01:44:52,960 --> 01:44:56,950
我死之前 我必须告诉你
I must confess before I die.

2077
01:44:57,120 --> 01:44:59,350
你说 头一档子
What was the first lie, then?

2078
01:44:59,720 --> 01:45:03,990
我…我能说这第二档子事儿吗？
Can I confess my second lie first?

2079
01:45:04,160 --> 01:45:05,300
好
Yes.

2080
01:45:05,560 --> 01:45:09,310
那谁…你还记得吗？
Do you still remember...

2081
01:45:51,880 --> 01:45:54,990
我弄不清楚你到底是老汤
I can't quite figure you out.

2082
01:45:55,800 --> 01:45:57,310
还是马邦德？
Counselor Tang or Governor Ma?

2083
01:45:58,240 --> 01:46:00,230
但是你没了
Now that you're gone,

2084
01:46:01,520 --> 01:46:03,350
张麻子也没了
"Pocky" Zhang, too, is no more.

2085
01:46:03,680 --> 01:46:07,630
真的也没了 假的也没了
Fact or fiction no longer matter now.

2086
01:46:08,840 --> 01:46:14,750
兄弟 我要帮你把这个县长当下去
For you, I'll go back and finish this war!

2087
01:46:16,040 --> 01:46:17,390
弟兄们
Brothers!

2088
01:46:18,160 --> 01:46:19,350
回鹅城！
March on Goose Town!

2089
01:46:24,000 --> 01:46:25,430
这个张麻子
This "Pocky" Zhang

2090
01:46:26,840 --> 01:46:28,910
杀了假麻子
has killed his imposter.

2091
01:46:29,840 --> 01:46:32,030
得了钱 不逃命
But instead of fleeing with the money,

2092
01:46:32,520 --> 01:46:35,080
莫非要跟我鱼死网破？
he wants a showdown with me.

2093
01:46:35,240 --> 01:46:37,070
那就请官兵来剿匪！
Let's get reinforcement.

2094
01:46:37,240 --> 01:46:38,950
我早就派胡百过去了
I've sent Hu Bai to fetch troops.

2095
01:46:39,120 --> 01:46:42,660
三天之后郭旅长的骑兵就到了
Cavalry will arrive in 3 days.

2096
01:46:45,600 --> 01:46:47,750
县长要斩黄四郎！
Governor swears to behead Huang,

2097
01:46:51,760 --> 01:46:54,220
谁人不想斩黄郎！
public enemy number one.

2098
01:46:57,000 --> 01:46:59,430
拐卖壮丁贩烟土！
Trades in opium and human misery,

2099
01:47:02,960 --> 01:47:05,590
杀了五任好县长！
Huang has killed five governors.

2100
01:47:09,120 --> 01:47:11,550
一成白银送你手！
The money that's been given out,

2101
01:47:15,040 --> 01:47:17,630
九成真金黄家藏！
is but one-tenth of his hoard!

2102
01:47:21,200 --> 01:47:23,500
邦德发誓三天内！
In memory of his dead comrades,

2103
01:47:26,960 --> 01:47:31,750
除暴安良祭老汤！
Ma will parade Huang's head in 3 days!

2104
01:47:37,280 --> 01:47:39,710
白花花的银子都散给了穷人
He gave away all his money to the poor.

2105
01:47:39,880 --> 01:47:41,070
作孽！
Disgraceful!

