01:59:58,880 --> 02:00:00,630
跪下！跪下！
Kneel down! Kneel!

2308
02:00:00,800 --> 02:00:01,780
别让我发脾气
Don't make me mad!

2309
02:00:01,960 --> 02:00:02,590
我数三下！
On my count of three!

2310
02:00:02,760 --> 02:00:03,670
一!
One!

2311
02:00:05,280 --> 02:00:06,340
二！
Two!

2312
02:00:07,080 --> 02:00:07,870
一！
One!

2313
02:00:08,240 --> 02:00:09,150
二！
Two!

2314
02:00:09,320 --> 02:00:11,510
谁？哪个欠打的？
What the...? Who's the son-of-a-bitch?

2315
02:00:11,680 --> 02:00:13,310
又想挨板子了是吧？
Want your ass kicked again?

2316
02:00:13,520 --> 02:00:15,030
大人 我讨厌吗？
Am I bothering you, sir?

2317
02:00:15,200 --> 02:00:17,150
如果我讨厌 我立马消失！
Say the word and I'll disappear.

2318
02:00:17,320 --> 02:00:19,750
如果不讨厌 我继续欺负他！
If not, I'll just carry on.

2319
02:00:20,760 --> 02:00:21,900
很讨厌
Go away.

2320
02:00:22,120 --> 02:00:23,910
大人 兄弟我就走了！
Right, we're going.

2321
02:00:24,080 --> 02:00:25,870
需要兄弟的时候 你吆喝一声
Just yell if you need me.

2322
02:00:26,040 --> 02:00:27,150
兄弟立马出现
Always at your service, sir.

2323
02:00:27,320 --> 02:00:30,150
告辞！告辞！走！
Goodbye, sir. Beat it!

2324
02:00:42,640 --> 02:00:43,950
下一步有什么打算？
What's next for you?

2325
02:00:44,120 --> 02:00:46,550
留在鹅城代替我？
Take my place here?

2326
02:00:48,920 --> 02:00:50,140
我不是家禽
I'm not a caged bird.

2327
02:00:51,400 --> 02:00:52,710
你是野兽
You're a predator.

2328
02:00:58,960 --> 02:01:02,350
进城那天 如果我亲自去接你
The day of your inauguration,

2329
02:01:02,640 --> 02:01:05,870
不是叫胡万过去给你捣乱
had I greeted you in person,

2330
02:01:07,040 --> 02:01:08,910
结果会不会不一样？
would things have turned out differently?

2331
02:01:09,160 --> 02:01:11,790
那帽子挺好 我喜欢
It was a nice hat. I liked it.

2332
02:01:12,040 --> 02:01:15,110
那不是最好的 我家里还有更好的
I have nicer ones at home.

2333
02:01:16,160 --> 02:01:17,270
转头送给你
I can give them to you.

2334
02:01:20,400 --> 02:01:22,150
一下子弄成了这样
Everything's gone in a flash.

2335
02:01:23,960 --> 02:01:25,990
你让我输得很惨啊！
You've totally wiped me out.

2336
02:01:27,800 --> 02:01:29,590
惨吗？黄老爷
It's not that bad.

2337
02:01:29,760 --> 02:01:31,310
你现在还抽着烟
You're still having a smoke,

2338
02:01:31,880 --> 02:01:33,430
还说着话
still chit-chatting.

2339
02:01:33,640 --> 02:01:39,630
可是六子 老二 师爷、夫人
But Six, Two, Counselor and his wife...

2340
02:01:40,080 --> 02:01:42,110
我听不到他们的声音了
I can no longer hear their voice.

2341
02:01:42,440 --> 02:01:45,550
而且永远听不到了
Never ever again.

2342
02:01:47,320 --> 02:01:48,950
你们四个人
Their four lives,

2343
02:01:49,800 --> 02:01:51,830
换我五代家业
in exchange for my heirloom,

2344
02:01:52,640 --> 02:01:53,430
不合算吗？
isn't that enough?

2345
02:01:53,640 --> 02:01:55,590
怎么算帐那是你的事
That's none of my business.

2346
02:01:55,920 --> 02:01:56,900
对我来说…
To me,

2347
02:01:57,440 --> 02:01:59,870
钱是钱 人是人
they are separate issues.

2348
02:02:00,280 --> 02:02:02,630
钱归了你 我认了
You could have kept the money.

2349
02:02:04,080 --> 02:02:05,910
为什么要散给他们？
But why did you give it away?

2350
02:02:07,680 --> 02:02:10,190
黄老爷 我问你个问题
Master Huang, let me ask you a question.

2351
02:02:10,520 --> 02:02:11,390
说
Shoot!

2352
02:02:12,120 --> 02:02:14,190
你说是钱对我重要
Which is more important to me?

2353
02:02:14,400 --> 02:02:15,670
还是你对我重要？
You or your fortune?

2354
02:02:16,840 --> 02:02:17,980
我
Me.

2355
02:02:19,680 --> 02:02:20,820
再想想
Think again.

2356
02:02:23,880 --> 02:02:25,270
不会是钱吧？
Can it be the money?

2357
02:02:26,360 --> 02:02:27,710
再想想
Think again.

2358
02:02:32,600 --> 02:02:33,950
还是我重要
I still think it's me.

2359
02:02:34,120 --> 02:02:37,270
你和钱对我都不重要
Neither matters to me.

2360
02:02:39,040 --> 02:02:40,180
那谁重要？
Then what is?

2361
02:02:44,200 --> 02:02:47,310
没有你 对我很重要
To rid of you is more important.

2362
02:02:57,880 --> 02:02:59,270
你不是找火柴吧？
Looking for a light?

2363
02:02:59,680 --> 02:03:00,350
不是
No.

2364
02:03:00,560 --> 02:03:02,030
那…
You must be...

2365
02:03:02,960 --> 02:03:04,310
你是找这个
Iooking for this.

2366
02:03:12,400 --> 02:03:13,590
你是个体面人
You're a man of honour.

2367
02:03:21,200 --> 02:03:22,420
只有一颗子弹
There's only one bullet left.

2368
02:03:24,120 --> 02:03:25,230
够
That's enough.

2369
02:03:25,920 --> 02:03:27,110
等等
Wait.

2370
02:03:27,640 --> 02:03:28,910
有话要我带给老汤？
Any message for Tang?

2371
02:03:29,080 --> 02:03:30,870
对了 告诉他…
Right, tell him...

2372
02:03:32,160 --> 02:03:33,510
我对不起他
I owe him an apology.

2373
02:03:34,160 --> 02:03:35,110
我骗了他
I lied to him.

2374
02:03:36,360 --> 02:03:37,750
你骗了他什么？
What was your lie?

2375
02:03:38,000 --> 02:03:40,300
我跟他说不回鹅城了
I said I wouldn't come back.

2376
02:03:40,760 --> 02:03:41,710
可是我回来了
But here I am.

2377
02:03:42,240 --> 02:03:43,220
你…
You...

2378
02:03:43,400 --> 02:03:44,950
你应该说到做到
You should have kept your promise.

2379
02:03:45,120 --> 02:03:46,950
是 我对不起他
Yes, I let him down.

2380
02:03:48,760 --> 02:03:50,150
可是我对你
But when it comes to you,

2381
02:03:50,920 --> 02:03:52,630
就要说到做到
I'll definitely keep my words.

2382
02:03:57,520 --> 02:03:58,710
明白
Understood.

2383
02:04:00,160 --> 02:04:01,750
明白！
Understood...

2384
02:04:10,880 --> 02:04:12,230
县长 县长…
Governor...

2385
02:04:12,840 --> 02:04:14,310
这两把椅子归我了
These chairs are mine.

2386
02:04:21,040 --> 02:04:22,950
大哥…
Chief...

2387
02:04:26,640 --> 02:04:27,670
别慌
Easy...

2388
02:04:28,080 --> 02:04:28,750
我能问你个问题吗？
Can I ask you a question?

2389
02:04:28,960 --> 02:04:29,870
说
Sure.

2390
02:04:31,280 --> 02:04:33,190
你喜欢花姐对吗？
You fancy Flora, right?

2391
02:04:34,120 --> 02:04:35,670
县长 县长
Governor,

2392
02:04:35,840 --> 02:04:37,710
我觉得我可以出现了
may I interrupt?

2393
02:04:38,040 --> 02:04:39,430
刚才我都听见了
I overheard everything.

2394
02:04:39,720 --> 02:04:41,670
他可不是个体面的人
Huang is not an honourable man.

2395
02:04:42,120 --> 02:04:43,550
我给了他一把手枪
I gave him a pistol.

2396
02:04:44,280 --> 02:04:46,270
他要是体面 你就让他体面
He can take his own life.

2397
02:04:46,640 --> 02:04:49,100
他要是不体面 你就帮他体面
If he doesn't, lend him a hand.

2398
02:04:49,280 --> 02:04:50,230
我明白！
Understood.

2399
02:04:50,400 --> 02:04:51,990
我有九种办法弄死他！
I have 9 ways to skin this cat!

2400
02:04:52,160 --> 02:04:53,350
九种！
Nine ways!

2401
02:04:54,960 --> 02:04:56,230
听我的雷声！
You'll hear my roar!

2402
02:04:57,120 --> 02:04:59,030
是有这么回事 怎么了？
Maybe just a little. Why?

2403
02:05:03,720 --> 02:05:05,110
千万别说是我说的
Don't say I tipped you off.

2404
02:05:09,800 --> 02:05:12,070
大哥 我们准备去上海了
Chief, we're off to Shanghai.

2405
02:05:12,320 --> 02:05:13,630
不跟我回山里了？
Not riding back with me?

2406
02:05:13,800 --> 02:05:14,860
还想回山里啊？
Still want to resume banditry?

2407
02:05:15,040 --> 02:05:16,590
您这腿脚都不利落了
You're too old for this.

2408
02:05:17,240 --> 02:05:19,670
怎么也不跟我打个招呼
You should've given me a heads-up.

2409
02:05:20,160 --> 02:05:21,870
这不正要跟您打招呼了嘛
That's what we're doing!

2410
02:05:22,920 --> 02:05:25,270
你不是要跟我当麻匪 到处发钱吗？
Didn't you want to be one of us?

2411
02:05:25,440 --> 02:05:27,110
今天不是把钱都发光了吗？
I just helped to dish out the money.

2412
02:05:27,280 --> 02:05:28,830
还有比今天更过瘾的？
I've never had a more satisfying day!

2413
02:05:29,080 --> 02:05:30,550
你看我都穿上这身了！
I'm even dressed for the part!

2414
02:05:31,720 --> 02:05:32,830
这么说…
So...

2415
02:05:34,040 --> 02:05:34,910
你改主意了？
you've changed your mind?

2416
02:05:35,080 --> 02:05:36,510
那还用说吗
That goes without saying!

2417
02:05:38,920 --> 02:05:40,950
老三 你有什么打算？
What's your plan, Three?

2418
02:05:41,960 --> 02:05:43,710
我要替二哥娶她
I'm going to marry her, on behalf of Two.

2419
02:05:45,840 --> 02:05:48,140
老二啊老二…
Two...

2420
02:05:48,920 --> 02:05:51,510
大哥 我是老三
Chief, I'm Three!

2421
02:05:54,560 --> 02:05:56,910
老三 你跟我在一起
Three, it no longer thrills you

2422
02:05:58,160 --> 02:06:00,110
-不高兴吗？     -高兴
- to ride with me? - Yes!

2423
02:06:00,640 --> 02:06:01,750
就是…
But...

2424
02:06:02,600 --> 02:06:03,870
有点不轻松
it's been hard going lately.

2425
02:06:05,720 --> 02:06:06,780
-你们俩呢？     -有点
- What about you? - We've had...

2426
02:06:06,960 --> 02:06:08,350
不轻松
better days.

2427
02:06:08,760 --> 02:06:09,590
老七呢？
Seven?

2428
02:06:14,080 --> 02:06:16,030
大哥…
Chief...

2429
02:06:17,560 --> 02:06:18,870
姑娘
Flora,

2430
02:06:19,880 --> 02:06:21,350
你这么拿着枪
hold your guns like this,

2431
02:06:21,960 --> 02:06:23,150
更好看
makes you look even cooler.

2432
02:06:28,760 --> 02:06:29,870
送你了
They're yours.

2433
02:06:32,520 --> 02:06:34,110
大哥 那我们先走一步啊！
Chief, we've got to go.

2434
02:06:34,280 --> 02:06:34,830
走了 大哥
Goodbye, Chief.

2435
02:06:35,000 --> 02:06:35,390
走！
Go!

2436
02:06:35,600 --> 02:06:37,310
走了 大哥
Bye, Chief!

2437
02:06:37,520 --> 02:06:39,630
别忘了下回跟我打个招呼啊
Give me a heads-up next time.

2438
02:06:39,800 --> 02:06:41,230
好 保重大哥
Chief, take care.

2439
02:06:41,440 --> 02:06:41,910
保重
Take care.

2440
02:06:42,000 --> 02:06:42,790
大哥再见
Goodbye, Chief!

2441
02:06:44,680 --> 02:06:45,820
大哥再见
Bye, Chief!

2442
02:06:48,600 --> 02:06:49,740
再见大哥
Bye, Chief!

2443
02:06:54,920 --> 02:06:58,230
张麻子！
"Pocky" Zhang!

2444
02:07:19,160 --> 02:07:23,510
老六 老二 师爷 夫人
Six, Two, Counselor, Madam...

2445
02:07:23,680 --> 02:07:25,110
你们看到了吧
Did you see that?

2446
02:08:13,360 --> 02:08:15,820
老三 去上海还是浦东？
Three, Shanghai or Pudong?

2447
02:08:16,640 --> 02:08:19,100
老三 去浦东还是上海？
Three, Pudong or Shanghai?

2448
02:08:19,440 --> 02:08:21,390
上海就是浦东！
Shanghai is Pudong!

2449
02:08:21,880 --> 02:08:24,550
浦东就是上海！
Pudong is Shanghai!

